20fired%20that%20I%20was%20burned%20out%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-costco-kroger-facing-self-checkout-reckoning-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-checkout%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20job%20was%20to%20monitor%20the%20self-checkout%20at%20our%20store%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20regular%20register%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20girls%20came%20through%20that%20night%20it%20happened.%20It%20was%20the%20fourth%20of%20November.%20They%20had%20a%20tote%2C%20one%20of%20those%20big%20gray%20plastic%20ones%20you%20store%20stuff%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20rang%20the%20tote%20up%2C%20which%20was%20%246.95.%20Then%20they%20walked%20right%20past%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20saying%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-amazon-lawsuits-employee-attendance-tracking-points-system-policy-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20know%20B.O.B.%20and%20L.I.S.A.%3F%26quot%3B%20B.O.B.%20is%20%26quot%3Bbottom%20of%20the%20basket.%26quot%3B%20L.I.S.A.%20is%20%26quot%3Blook%20inside%2C%20always.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20followed%20them%20and%20asked%20them%20if%20I%20could%20go%20and%20look%20inside%20the%20tote.%20They%20declined%20and%20tried%20to%20push%20their%20cart%20past%20me.%20I%20used%20my%20finger%20and%20flipped%20the%20lid%20off%20to%20where%20I%20could%20see%20inside.%20It%20was%20half-full%20of%20stuff%2C%20and%2090%25%20of%20it%20was%20makeup.%20And%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20know%20anything%20about%20cosmetics%2C%20but%20one%20little%20pencil%20is%20%2410%2C%20so%20the%20value%20of%20that%20tote%20added%20up%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20were%20called.%20But%20when%20they%20got%20there%2C%20they%20let%20the%20girls%20go.%20The%20asset%20protection%20team%20at%20the%20store%20didn't%20do%20anything%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20everything%20was%20going%20fine.%20Then%2C%20the%20guy%20in%20charge%20of%20asset%20protection%20and%20my%20supervisor%20called%20me%20in%20the%20office%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20into%20my%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20in%2C%20they%20referenced%20the%20%26quot%3Bincident%20with%20the%20girls%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20I%20was%20fired%2C%20just%20like%20that.%20They%20said%20I%20went%20against%20policy%20by%20stepping%20out%20of%20the%20door%20of%20the%20store%20and%20because%20I%20grabbed%20the%20tote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfterward%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20file%20for%20unemployment%2C%20but%20I%20found%20out%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Walmart%2C%20I%20wasn't%20eligible%20for%20it.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20through%20an%20appeal%20hearing%20because%20Walmart%20said%20they%20had%20a%20reason%20for%20firing%20me.%20I%20got%20that%20overturned%20in%20arbitration%20with%20Walmart%2C%20but%20if%20I%20hadn't%20appealed%20it%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20hearing%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20got%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheft%20was%20pretty%20common%20at%20the%20store%20where%20I%20worked.%20There%20was%20another%20incident%20I%20got%20a%20warning%20about.%20One%20woman%20swapped%20price%20tags%20so%20that%20a%20shirt%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20cost%20%248.95%20rang%20up%20for%20%241.%20I%20noticed%20it%2C%20so%20I%20walked%20over%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCould%20I%20look%20at%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20rang%20it%20up%20the%20right%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20customer%20walked%20over%20to%20customer%20service%20and%20told%20them%20that%20I%20was%20rude%2C%20that%20I%20insulted%20her%2C%20and%20that%20I%20accused%20her%20of%20stealing%2C%20which%20I%20never%20did.%20My%20boss%20said%20I%20was%20responsible%20for%20creating%20%26quot%3Ba%20dissatisfied%20customer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20made%20employees%20at%20my%20store%20wear%20this%20badge%20that%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-retail-shrink-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20shrinkage%20there%20has%20been%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20we're%20not%20doing%20our%20job%20to%20stop%20theft.%20I%20refused%20to%20wear%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20how%20it's%20gotten%20to%20be.%20These%20companies%20want%20you%20to%20prevent%20shoplifting%20and%20theft.%20But%20I%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20giving%20us%20the%20tools%20to%20do%20what%20you%20want%20us%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-wants-employees-own-more-stock-company-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20often%20can't%20do%20anything%20to%20stop%20shoplifters.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20policy%20is%20to%20let%20them%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20can't%20do%20that.%20I%20can't%20look%20and%20watch%20someone%20stealing%20something%20when%20the%20company%20talks%20about%20how%20that%20makes%20prices%20go%20up%20and%20puts%20my%20job%20in%20jeopardy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWalmart%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Walmart%20or%20another%20retailer%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-worker-fired-shoplifters-retail-theft-fight-problems-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708682401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6515a0b6c50dce00191346e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-worker-fired-shoplifters-retail-theft-fight-problems-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Walmart%20employee%20describes%20how%20she%20got%20fired%20after%20trying%20to%20stop%20shoplifters%20and%20says%20it%20reveals%20a%