oing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20overall%20tractor%20sales%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20ongoing%20fiscal%20year%20will%20see%20a%204%25%20or%205%25%20year-on-year%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20three%20states%20mentioned%20above%2C%20a%204%25%20decline%20in%20sales%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20tractor%20market%20in%20volume%20terms%2C%20over%20the%20first%20nine%20months%20of%20the%20fiscal%20year%20also%20pulled%20down%20the%20average%2C%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%206%25%20increase%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%9Cshored%20up%E2%80%9D%20overall%20numbers%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalytics%20company%20CRISIL%20said%20in%20a%20press%20note%20that%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20accounts%20for%20three%20quarters%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20tractors%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20sentiment%20largely%20drives%20this%20demand%2C%20which%20is%20in%20turn%20primarily%20influenced%20by%20the%20monsoons%20and%20rural%20income%2C%20CRISIL%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20factors%2C%20an%20uneven%20monsoon%20caused%20by%20the%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20weather%20pattern%20affected%20the%20figures%20this%20fiscal%20year.%20A%20poor%20geographic%20distribution%20of%20monsoon%20rains%20also%20marred%20the%20production%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekharif%3C%2Fem%3E%20crops%20this%20fiscal%20year%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20southern%20states%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisilratings.com%2Fen%2Fhome%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F02%2Fdomestic-tractor-volume-to-pick-up-3-5percent-next-fiscal.html%5C%22%3Ewhere%20tractor%20volumes%20declined%20by%2020%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CRISIL%E2%80%99s%20note%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20report%20said%20that%20poor%20rains%20and%20agricultural%20output%20tend%20to%20cause%20tractor%20purchase%20plans%20to%20be%20shelved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20cited%20dealers%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20Telangana%20%E2%80%93%20two%20states%20where%20tractor%20sales%20declined%20earlier%20this%20fiscal%20year%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20subsidy%20schemes%20in%20the%20respective%20states%20hit%20local%20farmers%E2%80%99%20purchasing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20report%20in%20the%20business%20newspaper%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20an%20executive%20at%20Mahindra%20and%20Mahindra%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20tractor%20manufacturer%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Findustry%2Fmanufacturing%2Ftractor-industry-in-a-rough-spot-mahindra-expects-sales-to-drop-10-in-q4-11707919780543.html%5C%22%3Etractor%20volumes%20would%20decline%20by%20roughly%2010%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20fourth%20and%20ongoing%20quarter%20of%20the%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Jejurikar%2C%20the%20executive%2C%20said%20that%20the%20overall%20decline%20in%20tractor%20volumes%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%20would%20reach%205%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20positives%20and%20negatives%20%5Bshaping%20rural%20demand%5D.%20The%20negatives%20are%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20a%20monsoon%20shortfall%20this%20year.%20Also%2C%20water%20reservoir%20levels%20are%20in%20the%20negative%20after%20many%20years.%20So%20we%E2%80%99re%205%25%20below%20LPA%20%5Blong%20period%20average%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20also%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20cited%20economists%20as%20saying%20that%20farmers%20may%20be%20deferring%20buying%20capital%20goods%20such%20as%20tractors%20until%20interest%20rates%20were%20lower%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20happen%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20different%20Mahindra%20executive%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20expectation%20of%20a%20good%20%3Cem%3Erabi%3C%2Fem%3E%20crop%20output%20and%20the%20government%20announcing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20estimate%E2%80%9D%20for%20horticulture%20production%20would%20help%20the%20rural%20economy%2C%20%E2%80%9Caid%20positive%20sentiments%20and%20support%20tractor%20demand%20in%20the%20coming%20months%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECRISIL%20cited%20one%20of%20its%20executives%20as%20saying%20that%20preliminary%20forecasts%20of%20a%20good%20monsoon%20for%202024%20%E2%80%9Caugurs%20well%20for%20rural%20sentiment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708676956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FPunjab-agriculture-Flickr-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ftractor-sales-saw-sharp-declines-in-telangana-maharashtra-and-karnataka-in-fy24-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tractor%20volumes%20also%20declined%20by%2020%25%20in%20the%20southern%20states%20in%20the%20ongoing%20fiscal%20year%20because%20of%20a%20poor%20monsoon%20and%20agricultural%20production%2C%20the%20CRISIL%20analytics%20firm%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ftractor-sales-saw-sharp-declines-in-telangana-maharashtra-and-karnataka-in-fy24-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20Blue%20Joins%20the%20Cult%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Finland%E2%80%99s%20Helsinki-Filmi%20%E2%80%93%20in%20%E2%80%98Kiss%20My%20Feet%2C%E2%80%99%20an%20Upcoming%20Series%20%E2%80%98a%20Bit%20Lighter%20Than%20%E2%80%98Midsommar%E2%80%99%26nbsp%3B(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708676951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F2-split-copia-4.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235920155%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amsterdam-based%20Big%20Blue%20is%20set%20to%20produce%2