by%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20midnight%2C%20two%20different%20rideshare%20vehicles%20were%20called%20to%20pick%20up%20Mr%20Dhawan%20outside%20Canopy%20Club%2C%20but%20he%20declined%20both%20rides%20despite%20attempts%20by%20venue%20staff%20and%20a%20passerby%20to%20convince%20him%20otherwise%2C%20the%20police%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubsequent%20phone%20calls%20and%20text%20messages%20sent%20by%20friends%20to%20Mr%20Dhawan's%20phone%20were%20not%20answered%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20information%20about%20his%20presence%20at%20Canopy%20Club%20was%20not%20communicated%20to%20them%20when%20the%20friend%2C%20who%20had%20been%20with%20him%20at%20Canopy%20Club%2C%20called%20them%20later%20in%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%2011%3A08%20am%20on%20January%2029%2C%20a%20university%20employee%20exiting%20Bevier%20Hall%20saw%20Mr%20Dhawan%20laying%20on%20concrete%20steps%20behind%201203%20W%20Nevada%20Street%20in%20Urbana%20and%20called%20the%20emergency%20telephone%20number%20911.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkul%20Dhawan's%20Parents%20Accuse%20Cops%20Of%20Negligence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkul%20Dhawan's%20parents%20have%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20school's%20police%20department%20for%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fparents-of-dead-indian-american-student-accuse-police-of-negligence-4941722%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsh%20Dhawan%20and%20Ritu%20Dhawan%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20their%20son%20was%20found%20just%20400%20feet%20from%20where%20he%20was%20reported%20missing%20based%20on%20location-tracking%20data%20on%20their%20son's%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20bizarre%2C%20that%20a%20kid%20is%20never%20found%20who%20was%20just%20less%20than%20a%20block%2C%20like%20one%20minute%20away%2C%20sitting%20there%2C%20dead%2C%20frozen%20to%20death%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ish%20Dhawan%20told%20T