.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20suffered%20a%20similar%20rupture%2C%20with%20the%20veteran's%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20joining%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-BJP%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20fears%20a%20similar%20exodus%20after%20two%20of%20its%20prominent%20leaders%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20and%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defections%20have%20complicated%20the%20seat%20negotiations%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20opposition%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20defections%2C%20wants%20a%20greater%20share%20in%20Mumbai%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sources%20assert%20that%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20are%20all%20determined%20to%20make%20it%20work%2C%20aware%20that%20for%20each%20party%2C%20it%20is%20a%20battle%20for%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20recently%20sealed%20difficult%20seat%20sharing%20deals%20with%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20redoubled%20efforts%20to%20close%20a%20deal%20with%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20refused%20to%20part%20with%20more%20than%20five%20of%20her%20state's%2042%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708663140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fqi63326o_rahul-gandhi-uddhav-thackeray-ani_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-dials-uddhav-thackeray-amid-maharashtra-seat-sharing-deadlock-5110918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Congress%20labours%20through%20intense%20seat%20negotiations%20with%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20election%2C%20Rahul%20Gan