%3BIt%20was%20a%20dress%20that%20other%20people%20had%20worn%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said%20during%20the%20Vogue%20interview.%20%26quot%3BMy%20stylist%20was%20like%2C%20'Please%20don't%20wear%20it.%20Somebody%20else%20has%20worn%20it.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221988%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Lopez%20at%20the%2042nd%20Annual%20Grammy%20Awards%20in%202000.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8092fce7f1785b2e354c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Lopez%20at%20the%2042nd%20Annual%20Grammy%20Awards%20in%202000.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Granitz%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20musician%20thought%20the%20dress%20looked%20great%20and%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20it%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20you%20bought%20it%2C%20and%20it%20looks%20the%20best%2C%20so%20I'm%20going%20to%20wear%20it.'%20And%20so%20I%20did.%20And%20it%20caused%20quite%20a%20stir%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20singer%20then%20compared%20her%20Versace%20gown%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarilyn-monroe-daring-looks-that-made-her-hollywood-fashion-icon-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarilyn%20Monroe's%20white%20halter%20dress%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Seven%20Year%20Itch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20every%20generation%20needs%20its%20iconic%20kind%20of%20Marilyn%20dress%2C%20and%20this%20is%20that%20dress%20for%20this%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20it%20became%20that%3F%20It%20was%20just%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20wind%20blew%20open%2C%20and%20I%20walked%20out%20onto%20the%20stage%2C%20and%20it%20just%20kinda%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222406%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Lopez%20at%20the%2042nd%20Annual%20Grammy%20Awards.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8099fce7f1785b2e354cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222940%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Lopez%20at%20the%2042nd%20Annual%20Grammy%20Awards.%20This%20image%20shows%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Versace%20gown.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Granitz%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20Lopez%20walked%20the%20red%20carpet%20with%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grammy.com%2Fartists%2Fjennifer-lopez%2F14846%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearned%20her%20first%20Grammy%20nomination%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Best%20Dance%20Recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etonline.com%2Ffashion%2F208732_jennifer_lopez_says_walking_the_red_carpet_her_iconic_grammy_dress_was_weird%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEntertainment%20Tonight%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Carly%20Steel%20that%20she%20felt%20people%20stirring%20when%20she%20stepped%20on%20the%20red%20carpet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20weird%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'What's%20happening%3F'%20And%20my%20dress%20was%20happening%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20singer%20was%20not%20the%20first%20person%20to%20wear%20the%20dress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20semi-sheer%20number%20was%20revealed%20at%20the%20Versace%20spring-summer%20runway%20show%20during%20Milan%20Fashion%20Week%20in%20October%201999%2C%20where%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYI9Y--sVqCQ%26ab_channel%3DVogue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworn%20by%20model%20Amber%20Valletta%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%201999%2C%20Donatella%20Versace%20herself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gettyimages.co.uk%2Fdetail%2Fnews-photo%2Fitalian-fashion-designer-donatella-versace-at-the-1999-rock-news-photo%2F635927441%3Fadppopup%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewore%20the%20gown%20to%20the%20Rock%20Style%20Gala%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Metropolitan%20Museum%20of%20Art%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202000%2C%20about%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Grammys%2C%20Geri%20Halliwell%20of%20the%20Spice%20Girls%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gettyimages.co.uk%2Fdetail%2Fnews-photo%2Fbritish-singer-geri-halliwell-of-the-spice-girls-at-the-1st-news-photo%2F74685762%3Fadppopup%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewore%20the%20dress%20to%20the%201st%20Annual%20NRJ%20Music%20Awards%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Cannes%2C%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Lopez%20wasn't%20the%20first%20to%20wear%20the%20dress%2C%20she%20was%20the%20one%20who%20made%20it%20iconic%20%E2%80%94%20so%20much%20so%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-lopezs-versace-grammys-dress-inspired-google-image-search-2015-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Image%20Search%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20created%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202015%2C%20former%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20wrote%20in%20an%20article%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.project-syndicate.org%2Fmagazine%2Fgoogle-european-commission-and-disruptive-technological-change-by-eric-schmidt-2015-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProject%20Syndicate%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20Lopez's%20green%20dress%20moment%20inspired%20the%20Google%20founders%20to%20create%20Google%20Image%20Search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20people%20wanted%20more%20than%20just%20text.%20This%20first%20became%20apparent%20after%20the%202000%20Grammy%20Awards%2C%20where%20Jennifer%20Lopez%20wore%20a%20green%20dress%20that%2C%20well%2C%20caught%20the%20world's%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20search%20query%20we%20had%20ever%20seen.%20But%20we%20had%20no%20surefire%20way%20of%20getting%20users%20exactly%20what%20they%20wanted%3A%20J%C2%ADLo%20wearing%20that%20dress.%20Google%20Image%20Search%20was%20born.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-lopez-stylist-green-versace-dress-google-image-search-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708662663000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8088490413ab8e1d64678%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-lopez-stylist-green-versace-dress-google-image-search-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20jungle-print%20Versace%20dress%20that%20Jennifer%20Lopez%20wore%20to%20the%20Grammys%20in%202000%20inspired%20Google%20Image%20Search%2C%20former%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20said%20in%202015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A85%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-lopez-stylist-green-versace-dress-google-image-search-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGood%20Night.%20Malaysian%20370%26quot%3B%3A%20World's%20Top%20Missing%20Plane%20Mystery%2C%2010%20Years%20On%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20Night.%20Malaysian%20Three%20Seven%20Zero.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20six%20words%20were%20the%20last%20radio%20transmission%20from%20the%20cockpit%20of%20Malaysia%20Airlines%20Flight%20370%2C%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20aircraft%20took%20off%20late%20at%20night%20from%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20to%20Beijing%20on%20March%208%2C%202014.%20Minutes%20later%2C%20the%20plane%20disappeared%20from%20air-traffic%20control%20radar%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20huge%20Boeing%20Co.%20777%20jet%2C%20almost%20as%20long%20as%20a%20Manhattan%20city%20block%20and%20taller%20than%20a%20five-story%20building%2C%20had%20somehow%20managed%20to%20make%20itself%20invisible%20in%20the%20clear%20night%20sky.%20There%20were%20239%20people%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsuing%20search%20operations%20combed%20through%20some%20of%20the%20deepest%20ocean%20floors%20in%20the%20inhospitable%20southern%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20off%20Australia's%20western%20seaboard%2C%20and%20found%20no%20trace%20of%20the%20main%20fuselage%20or%20any%20passengers%20and%20crew.%20Of%20the%203%20million%20components%20in%20the%20777%2C%20just%20a%20few%20fragments%20washed%20ashore%20years%20later%20on%20the%20east%20African%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20mayday%20call%2C%20no%20known%20flight%20path%20and%20no%20wreckage%2C%20MH370%20remains%20modern%20aviation's%20biggest%20mystery.%20And%20while%20investigators%20had%20very%20little%20to%20go%20on%2C%20they%20were%20clear%20on%20one%20thing%3A%20A%20plane%20must%20never%20go%20missing%20like%20this%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2010%20years%20on%2C%20an%20industrywide%20push%20to%20rule%20out%20a%20similar%20case%20has%20been%20stymied%20by%20bureaucracy%2C%20financial%20pressure%2C%20and%20a%20debate%20about%20who%20should%20have%20ultimate%20control%20of%20the%20cockpit%2C%20according%20to%20years%20of%20regulatory%20amendments%20chronicling%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20aircraft-tracking%20tool%20that%20was%20proposed%20by%20Malaysian%20authorities%20weeks%20after%20the%20disaster%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20implemented.%20While%20the%20industry%20has%20saved%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20equipment%20costs%2C%20there%20remains%20an%20ocean-sized%20hole%20in%20aviation's%20safety%20protocols%2C%20meaning%20that%20a%20doomed%20passenger%20jet%20in%20a%20remote%20corner%20of%20the%20planet%20could%20remain%20hidden%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20search%20teams%20looked%20in%20vain%20for%20MH370%2C%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20safety%20regulation%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20International%20Civil%20Aviation%20Organization%20proposed%20new%20jets%20should%20broadcast%20their%20position%20at%20least%20every%20minute%20if%20they%20were%20in%20trouble.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20give%20authorities%20early%20warning%20of%20an%20unfolding%20disaster.%20Should%20the%20plane%20later%20go%20down%2C%20rescue%20teams%20would%20at%20least%20have%20a%20chance%20of%20locating%20the%20crash%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn't%20turned%20out%20that%20way.%20The%20one-minute%20tracking%20rule%20has%20twice%20been%20delayed.%20It%20was%20initially%20due%20to%20be%20in%20force%20in%20January%202021%20but%20is%20now%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20from%20January%202025.%20Bloomberg%20News%20asked%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20major%20airlines%20spanning%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Asia%20how%20many%20planes%20in%20their%20fleets%20already%20meet%20ICAO's%20requirements.%20At%20the%20airlines%20that%20responded%2C%20very%20few%20planes%20are%20compliant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20France%2C%20which%20had%20more%20than%20250%20aircraft%20as%20of%20September%2C%20said%20seven%20jets%20-%20all%20Airbus%20SE%20A350s%20-%20comply%20with%20the%20standard.%20Korean%20Air%20Lines%20Co.%20said%20three%20of%20its%20159-strong%20fleet%20are%20equipped%20with%20the%20tracking%20device%2C%20while%20Japan%20Airlines%20Co.%20said%20two%20of%20its%20226%20planes%20have%20the%20technology%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20since%20MH370%20vanished%20has%20been%20unacceptable%2C%20said%20Hassan%20Shahidi%2C%20president%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20the%20Flight%20Safety%20Foundation%2C%20a%20Virginia-based%20not-for-profit%20group%20that%20promotes%20aviation%20safety%20standards.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20tragedy%20and%20solutions%20have%20been%20developed.%20It%20is%20absolutely%20imperative%20that%20we%20take%20this%20final%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20Shahidi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20being%20years%20late%2C%20the%20fresh%20tracking%20standard%20applies%20only%20to%20new%20aircraft.%20There's%20no%20requirement%20to%20install%20the%20relevant%20technology%20on%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20older%20planes%20in%20service%20as%20of%20last%20year.%20That%20means%20thousands%20of%20aircraft%20will%20fly%20for%20decades%2C%20ferrying%20millions%20of%20passengers%20around%20the%20world%2C%20without%20a%20capability%20that%20was%20deemed%20crucial%20after%20MH370%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20hurdles%20have%20played%20at%20least%20some%20role%20in%20the%20delays.%20When%20the%20US%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20recommended%20%26quot%3Btamper-proof%26quot%3B%20tracking%20systems%20on%20planes%20in%202015%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20considered%20the%20global%20pacesetter%20for%20the%20civil%20aviation%20industry%2C%20pushed%20back.%20The%20FAA%20said%20it%20couldn't%20be%20done%20without%20sacrificing%20the%20pilot's%20control%20of%20all%20systems%2C%20considered%20a%20mainstay%20of%20aviation%20safety%20protocols%20because%20pilots%20should%20have%20final%20say%20over%20the%20aircraft%20in%20case%20of%20emergencies.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20MH370%20Captain%20Zaharie%20Ahmad%20Shah%20has%20been%20a%20major%20focus%20point%20of%20the%20mystery.%20According%20to%20the%20presumed%20sequence%20of%20events%20in%20the%20final%20report%2C%20the%20plane%20deliberately%20left%20its%20planned%20route%20north%20to%20China%2C%20looped%20back%20over%20Malaysia%20and%20headed%20out%20to%20sea.%20It%20cruised%20south%20for%20about%20six%20hours%20and%20probably%20came%20down%20in%20the%20southern%20Indian%20Ocean%20when%20it%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20managed%20to%20roughly%20map%20the%20doomed%20jet's%20route%20by%20studying%20its%20hourly%20connections%20with%20a%20satellite%2036%2C000%20kilometers%20(22%2C400%20miles)%20above%20Earth.%20As%20remarkable%20as%20this%20detective%20work%20was%2C%20it%20produced%20an%20enormous%20potential%20crash%20zone.%20An%20international%20search%20fleet%20surveyed%20710%2C000%20square%20kilometers%20of%20seabed%2C%20peppered%20with%20trenches%20and%20peaks%2C%20before%20the%20hunt%20was%20called%20off%20in%202017.%20A%20fresh%20effort%20the%20following%20year%20by%20marine%20exploration%20company%20Ocean%20Infinity%20also%20came%20up%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forensic%20detail%20included%20in%20the%20450-page%20final%20report%20into%20the%20tragedy%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20escape%20the%20human%20toll%20of%20the%20tragedy.%20The%20report%20lists%20the%20seat%20number%2C%20gender%20and%20nationality%20of%20the%20passengers.%20The%20economy%20section%20was%20almost%20full%2C%20two%20children%20sat%20in%2017F%20and%2018F%20and%20another%20in%2030H%2C%20and%20there%20were%20two%20infants%20on%20board.%20In%20the%20rear%2C%20four%20rows%20apart%2C%20two%20Iranians%20were%20traveling%20on%20stolen%20European%20passports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20business-class%20section%20was%20barely%20one-third%20occupied%2C%20with%20most%20of%20the%2010%20passengers%20seated%20by%20the%20windows.%20The%2010%20flight%20attendants%20tending%20to%20their%20guests%20all%20came%20from%20Malaysia%2C%20while%20the%20majority%20of%20passengers%20were%20Chinese.%20Just%20after%201%20a.m.%2C%20the%20flight%20had%20settled%20into%20cruising%20altitude%20of%2035%2C000%20feet.%20Some%2020%20minutes%20later%2C%20MH370%20signed%20off%20from%20Malaysian%20air-traffic%20control%20with%20its%20last-ever%20voice%20transmission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20said%20it's%20possible%20someone%20then%20switched%20off%20the%20plane's%20communications%20systems%2C%20while%20stopping%20short%20of%20a%20definitive%20conclusion.%20The%20team%20was%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20determine%20the%20real%20cause%20for%20the%20disappearance%20of%20MH370%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20report%20made%20an%20impassioned%20appeal%20to%20the%20international%20aviation%20community%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20to%20provide%20assurance%20to%20the%20traveling%20public%20that%20the%20location%20of%20current-generation%20commercial%20aircraft%20is%20always%20known.%20It%20is%20unacceptable%20to%20do%20otherwise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one-minute%20tracking%20rule%20was%20designed%20to%20resolve%20that%20blind%20spot%2C%20by%20aiming%20to%20nail%20down%20a%20crash%20site%20to%20within%20a%20radius%20of%20six%20nautical%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20still%20not%20good%20enough%2C%20said%20Mike%20Poole%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20APS%20Aerospace%20Corp.%2C%20an%20Ottawa-based%20company%20that%20conducts%20flight-data%20analysis%20for%20accident%20investigations.%20With%20satellites%20covering%20almost%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20planet%2C%20Poole%20wants%20all%20commercial%20flights%20to%20transmit%20their%20position%20and%20other%20key%20data%20almost%20constantly%20over%20a%20tamper-proof%20system.%20It%20shouldn't%20matter%20whether%20the%20aircraft's%20in%20trouble%20or%20not%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20event%20of%20a%20missing%20plane%2C%20not%20only%20do%20you%20know%20where%20it%20is%2C%20you%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20instant%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Poole%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20the%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20of%20Canada%20for%20more%20than%2020%20years%20and%20led%20its%20flight-recorder%20laboratory.%20%26quot%3BYou%20would%20probably%20have%20a%20really%20good%20idea%20what%20happened%20to%20MH370.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinding%20any%20missing%20plane%20is%20important%20because%20understanding%20the%20cause%20of%20past%20incidents%20is%20central%20to%20preventing%20disasters%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20FAA%20has%20an%20online%20library%20devoted%20to%20lessons%20learned%20from%20decades%20of%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20MH370%20disappeared%20in%202014%2C%20there%20was%20an%20initial%20flurry%20of%20activity.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association%2C%20an%20airline%20trade%20group%2C%20formed%20a%20task%20force%20to%20draw%20up%20proposals%20for%20more%20stringent%20flight%20monitoring.%20Boeing%2C%20Airbus%20and%20ICAO%2C%20a%20United%20Nations%20agency%20central%20to%20aviation%20standard-setting%2C%20were%20all%20included.%20One%20of%20the%20outcomes%20from%20this%20early%20work%20was%20a%20requirement%20for%20large%2C%20new%20passenger%20planes%20in%20distress%20to%20transmit%20their%20position%20at%20least%20once%20a%20minute%20from%20Jan.%201%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeeting%20that%20deadline%20was%20beyond%20the%20sector.%20In%20a%20four-page%20submission%20to%20ICAO%20in%202019%2C%20Australian%20authorities%20claimed%20there%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20lack%20of%20coordination%20and%20information%20sharing%26quot%3B%20between%20Montreal-based%20ICAO%20and%20search-and-rescue%20entities.%20One-minute%20tracking%20was%20subsequently%20delayed%20until%202023.%20When%20the%20coronavirus%20shut%20down%20air%20travel%20and%20sent%20hundreds%20of%20newly%20made%2C%20undelivered%20planes%20into%20storage%2C%20the%20tracking%20rule%20was%20shunted%20back%20to%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202022%20filing%20by%20the%20European%20Union%20Aviation%20Safety%20Agency%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20financial%20gains%20from%20the%20second%20delay.%20The%20EASA%20document%20said%20the%20International%20Coordinating%20Council%20of%20Aerospace%20Industry%20Associations%2C%20representing%20plane%20manufacturers%2C%20asked%20ICAO%20for%20the%20postponement.%20EASA%20cited%20estimated%20cost%20savings%20of%20between%20%24175%20million%20and%20%24262%20million%20-%20less%20than%20the%20list%20price%20of%20a%20new%20Boeing%20777.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20EASA%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20technology%20to%20process%20emergency%20signals%20by%20the%20satellite%20networks%20has%20faced%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20delays%26quot%3B%20because%20the%20satellites%20needed%20to%20monitor%20the%20entire%20globe%20weren't%20yet%20fully%20operable.%20And%20the%20entities%20responsible%20for%20acting%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20distress%20report%20also%20need%20time%20to%20set%20up%20processes%20to%20handle%20such%20incidents%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMontreal-based%20ICCAIA%20declined%20to%20comment.%20An%20Airbus%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20delays%20and%20deferred%20to%20the%20EASA%20filing.%20ICAO%20said%20in%20an%20email%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20pandemic%20put%20everyone%20back.%26quot%3B%20Tracking%20equipment%20for%20planes%20in%20distress%20might%20someday%20be%20obligatory%20on%20older%20aircraft%2C%20%26quot%3Bdepending%20on%20how%20essential%20and%20performing%20the%20new%20device%20turns%20out%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20ICAO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20said%20it%20continues%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20under%20the%20oversight%20of%20global%20regulators%20on%20the%20requirement%20for%20a%20Global%20Aeronautical%20Distress%20and%20Safety%20System.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20airlines%20tightened%20their%20tracking%20capabilities%20to%20some%20degree%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20MH370%2C%20pinpointing%20their%20large%20passenger%20planes%20at%20least%20every%2015%20minutes%20when%20over%20remote%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20job%20on%20safety%20is%20never%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20IATA%20Director%20General%20Willie%20Walsh.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20events%20like%20MH370%2C%20I%20think%20it%20really%20does%20cause%20everybody%20to%20stand%20back%20and%20say%2C%20'How%20can%20this%20happen%3F'%20Could%20this%20happen%20again%3F%20I'd%20be%20very%20surprised%20if%20it%20could.%20I'm%20not%20saying%20the%20chances%20are%20zero%2C%20but%20the%20chances%20are%20so%20much%20smaller%20today%20than%20they%20were%2010%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOff-the-shelf%20products%20that%20track%20commercial%20flights%20continuously%20are%20available.%20Inmarsat%20and%20Aireon%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20provide%20carriers%20near%20real-time%20in-flight%20data%20using%20a%20network%20of%20satellites%20that%20can%20link%20up%20with%20planes%20almost%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20with%20high%20precision%20and%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20a%20situation%20like%20the%202009%20crash%20of%20Air%20France%20447%20-%20a%20functional%20plane%20that%20plunged%20into%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20without%20suspicion%20of%20foul%20play%20and%20was%20only%20found%20after%20two%20years%20-%20should%20theoretically%20never%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICAO%20lays%20down%20clear%20requirements%20for%20in-flight%20one-minute%20tracking%20devices%20for%20aircraft%20in%20trouble.%20They%20need%20to%20activate%20in%20a%20range%20of%20scenarios%2C%20such%20as%20a%20loss%20of%20propulsion.%20Critically%2C%20devices%20triggered%20automatically%20can't%20be%20manually%20turned%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirbus%20introduced%20an%20emergency%20locator%20transmitter%20system%20that%20meets%20the%20standard%2C%20and%20has%20fitted%20it%20on%20all%20new%20widebody%20aircraft%20the%20planemaker%20has%20delivered%20since%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20such%20capability%20on%20Malaysia%20Airlines%20Flight%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Hattley%2C%20an%20Australian%20air-accident%20expert%20who%20joined%20the%20international%20investigation%20team%20in%20Malaysia%20after%20MH370%20went%20missing%2C%20says%20the%20mystery%20still%20hangs%20over%20him%2C%20even%20after%2010%20years.%20While%20the%20incident%20bore%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20a%20deliberate%20action%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%20frustrates%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20about%20MH370%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hattley.%20%26quot%3BAs%20an%20accident%20investigator%2C%20your%20job%20is%20to%20answer%20questions%2C%20provide%20answers%20to%20families%2C%20friends%20and%20n