campus.%20Attempts%20by%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20get%20a%20response%20from%20Parul%20University%20authorities%20failed.%20Here%20is%20a%20video%20of%20the%20brawl%20between%20local%20and%20African%20students%20on%20the%20Parul%20University%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FForeign%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Foreign%3C%2Fa%3E%20students%20assaulted%20at%20Parul%20University%20in%20Gujarat.%20These%20international%20students%20are%20at%20Parul%20University%20on%20an%20exchange%20programme.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FParulUniversity%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ParulUniversity%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fparuluniversity%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23paruluniversity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fgujarat%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23gujarat%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fvibesofindia%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23vibesofindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkJ5XuTt0X8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkJ5XuTt0X8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Vibes%20of%20India%20(%40vibesofindia_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvibesofindia_%2Fstatus%2F1760593065712947333%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20not%20confirm%20the%20exact%20day%20and%20time%20of%20the%20footage%2C%20but%20confirmed%20the%20incident.%20Parul%20University%20did%20not%20approach%20the%20police%20and%20the%20issue%20was%20%E2%80%9Csettled%E2%80%9D%20internally%2C%20a%20university%20student%20told%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20No%20campus%20security%20intervened%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20student%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParul%20University%20chose%20not%20to%20issue%20any%20official%20statement%20on%20this%20issue.%20Parul%20University%20is%20notorious%20for%20its%20misleading%20claims%2C%20unsavoury%20campus%20incidents%20and%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%2C%20founded%20in%202009%2C%20has%20been%20seen%20controversy%20for%20one%20or%20the%20other%2C%20time%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3Enews%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20a%20paper%20leak%20scandal%20just%20months%20ago%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20student%20and%20an%20office%20assistant.%20Examination%20papers%20of%20the%20university%20could%20easily%20be%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20the%20varsity%20suspended%2040%20students%20for%20a%20month%20as%20they%20had%20raised%20concern%20over%20spreading%20Covid-19%20on%20the%20campus%20and%20the%20university%20insisting%20on%20higher%20fees%20and%20declining%20online%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20in%20June%202022%2C%20even%20as%20entire%20Gujarat%20was%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20Covid-19%20and%20there%20were%20over%2032%2C000%20active%20cases%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Parul%20University%20forced%20its%20students%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20campus.%20More%20than%2065%20students%20caught%20the%20infection%20but%20the%20management%20stubbornly%20refused%20to%20go%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngry%20students%2C%20miffed%20at%20the%20insensitive%20management%2C%20got%20together%20and%20protested%20against%20the%20decision.%20The%20management%20in%20turn%20instructed%20their%20security%20guards%20to%20%E2%80%9Cgive%20a%20good%20dose%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20students.%20The%20guards%20got%20into%20a%20physical%20fistfight%20with%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%20the%20students%20stormed%20the%20campus%20to%20demand%20the%20university%20move%20to%20online%20teaching.%20Videos%20from%20the%20campus%20showed%20the%20students%20clashing%20with%20the%20security%20guards%20outside%20the%20main%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20IAS%20officer%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20worked%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20had%20at%20that%20time%20informed%20Vo!%20of%20many%20other%20irregularities%20going%20on%20at%C2%A0%20Parul%20University%20and%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20have%20political%20blessings%20and%20hence%20they%20go%20scot-free%20despite%20being%20a%20third%20class%20place%20of%20learning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotorious%20for%20buying%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20university%20%E2%80%9D%20rankings%20and%20ratings%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fparul-university-now-cheats-income-tax-misuses-data-and-appoints-178-students-as-directors-and-trustees-to-evade-taxparul-university-now-cheats-income-tax-misuses-data-and-appoints-178-students-as-di%2F%5C%22%3Eincome%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20department%20had%20put%20Parul%20University%20under%20the%20radar%20for%20misusing%20documents%20of%20at%20least%20200%20college%20students.%20To%20save%20tax%2C%20the%20university%2C%20which%20naturally%20would%20collect%20all%20documents%20of%20its%20students%20during%20admissions%2C%20made%20at%20least%20178%20students%20%E2%80%9CDirectors%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CTrustees%E2%80%9D.%20They%20filed%20these%20fake%20declarations%20with%20the%20income%20tax%20authorities.%20The%20department%20has%20registered%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20President%20and%20Trustees%20of%20Parul%20University%20and%20Parul%20Arogya%20Seva%20Mandal%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Benami%20Property%20Transaction%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Pandya%2C%20an%20officer%20in%20the%20Parul%20Arogya%20Seva%20Mandal%20Trust%20since%20August%204%2C%202003%2C%20was%20officially%20grilled%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20officials%20in%20this%20matter.%20The%20confirmed%20statement%20of%20Pandya%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cignorant%20about%20these%20employees%20being%20paid%20salary.%20He%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20their%20recruitment%20procedure.%20Their%20attendance%20was%20not%20monitored%20by%20him%20since%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20these%20salary%20payments.%E2%80%9D%20Though%20he%20looked%20after%20salary%20payments%20of%20all%20employees%2C%20he%20denied%20payment%20to%20these%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParul%20Patel%2C%20Managing%20Trustee%20of%20Parul%20University%2C%20had%20confessed%20in%20her%20recorded%20statement%20to%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20that%20bogus%20expenses%20were%20booked%20as%20salaries%20paid%20to%20ghost%20employees%20on%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20register.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20university%20was%20founded%20by%20Jayesh%20Patel.%20A%20political%20turncoat%2C%20Jayesh%20was%20with%20the%20BJP%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20for%20raping%20a%20student%20in%202016.%20The%20student%2C%20a%2021%20year%20old%20from%20a%20poor%20family%2C%20was%20studying%20in%20Parul%20University%E2%80%99s%20nursing%20college%20and%20bravely%20came%20forward%20to%20complain%20against%20the%20university%20founder%20and%20trustee%2C%20Jayesh%20Patel%2C%20then%2066%20years%20old%20within%2024%20hours%20after%20she%20was%20raped.%20Jayesh%20was%20then%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20who%20promptly%20dismissed%20him%20after%20his%20DNA%20profiling%20confirmed%20the%20rape.%20He%20was%20subsequently%20arrested%20by%20Gujarat%20police.%20Jayesh%20had%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202014.%20He%20had%20flirted%20with%20several%20other%20parties%2C%20including%20Congress%2C%20in%20the%20past.%20He%20had%20even%20contested%20assembly%20elections%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayesh%2C%20a%20diploma%20holder%20in%20homeopathy%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20used%20to%20run%20a%20walk-in%20clinic%20in%20Kothi%20area%20of%20Vadodara%20and%20his%20main%20occupation%20was%20to%20allegedly%20carry%20out%20illegal%20abortions%20for%20Rs%20150.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20set%20up%20a%20homeopathy%20institution%20in%C2%A0Ahmedabad%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20sprawling%20campus%20of%20Parul%20University%2C%20named%20after%20his%20eldest%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20sensational%20Parul%20University%20Rape%20Case%2C%20the%20police%20had%20also%20arrested%20then-nursing%20hostel%20warden%20Bhavna%20Patel.%20Bhavna%20was%20alleged%20to%20be%20assigned%20to%20bring%20new%20girls%20to%20the%20Parul%20University%20founder%20Jayesh%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20very%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20only%20interested%20in%20girls%20below%2022%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nursing%20student%20who%20had%20registered%20the%20police%20complaint%20had%20said%20in%20her%20FIR%20that%20Bhavna%20Patel%20took%20her%20to%20university%20founder%20Jayesh%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20house%20during%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20June%2016%20and%20June%2017.%20The%20victim%20had%20also%20mentioned%20in%20her%20FIR%20that%20Jayesh%20Patel%20had%20threatened%20to%20rusticate%20her%20from%20the%20institute%20and%20spoil%20her%20career%20by%20failing%20her%20in%20exams%20if%20she%20revealed%20it%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20lodged%20at%20Waghodia%20police%20station%20against%20them%20under%20sections%20376%20(rape)%2C%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20114%20(abetting%20the%20crime)%2C%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20IPC%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20after%20her%20rape%2C%20the%20Surat%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20Monday%20confirmed%20to%20the%20Vadodara%20police%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20right%20and%20she%20was%20indeed%20raped%20by%20Jayesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20Local%20Crime%20Branch%20(LCB)%20police%20inspector%20and%20the%20investigating%20officer%2C%20K.J.%20Chaudhari%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20the%20medical%20reports%20from%20the%20FSL%20Surat.%20The%20results%20of%20all%20the%20tests%20are%20positive.%20The%20DNA%20profiling%20is%20matching.%20The%20reports%20have%20confirmed%20that%20Patel%20raped%20the%20victim.%20Jayesh%20Patel%20who%20had%20absconded%20had%20been%20arrested%20from%20nearby%20Anand.%20Jayesh%20Patel%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20died%20of%20kidney%20failure%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20Ahmedabad%20where%20he%20was%20in%20police%20custody%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20his%20son%20Devanshu%20Patel%20runs%20the%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fafrican-students-on-exchange-programme-assaulted-on-parul-university-campus-in-vadodara%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20Vibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708661857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23094718%2FParul-University-selects-Veeam-to-Ensure-Data-Availability-for-Students-Faculty-and-Staff-930x527-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgujarat-african-exchange-students-abused-with-slurs-assaulted-in-vadodara%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parul%20University%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20occurred%2C%20has%20a%20history%20of%20controversy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgujarat-african-exchange-students-abused-with-slurs-assaulted-in-vadodara%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Everything%20we%20know%20about%20'True%20Detective'%20season%205%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22danvers%20in%20true%20detective%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%20with%20a%20mug%20on%20the%20table%2C%20wearing%20her%20police%20uniform%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7cceb90413a