0to%20pressurise%20the%20government%20to%20enact%20a%20promised%20law%20on%20minimum%20support%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%2C%20information%20and%20broadcasting%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said%20that%20the%20new%20FRP%2C%20which%20will%20be%20effective%20in%20the%20next%20sugarcane%20season%20from%20October%201%2C%202024%2C%20will%20be%20Rs%20340%20at%20the%20sugarcane%20recovery%20rate%20of%2010.25%25.%20This%20amounts%20to%20an%20increase%20of%20Rs%2025%20from%20the%20existing%20Rs%20315%20per%20quintal%20of%20sugarcane%20crop.%20The%20farmers%20will%20get%20an%20additional%20price%20of%20Rs%203.32%20per%20quintal%20for%20each%20increase%20of%20sugar%20recovery%20by%200.1%25%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20same%20amount%20will%20also%20be%20deducted%20for%20every%200.1%25%20drop%20from%20the%20benchmark%20figure%20of%2010.25%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recovery%20rate%2C%20expressed%20in%20percentage%2C%20is%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20ratio%20between%20sugar%20produced%20and%20the%20sugarcane%20crushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20said%20that%20the%20FRP%20price%20hike%20of%20Rs%2025%20is%20the%20highest%20since%202014-15%2C%20when%20Modi%20first%20came%20to%20power%2C%20and%20is%20therefore%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fcabinet-hike-in-sugarcane-procurement-price-to-rs-340-per-quintal-9173915%2F%5C%22%3ECentre%E2%80%99s%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20decision%20is%20%E2%80%9Cgoing%20to%20benefit%20more%20than%205%20crore%20sugarcane%20farmers%20(including%20family%20members)%20and%20lakhs%20of%20other%20persons%20involved%20in%20the%20sugar%20sector%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20claiming%20that%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cre-confirms%20fulfillment%20of%20Modi%20ki%20Guarantee%20to%20double%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%3Cem%3Ejumla%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20making%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20hike%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20multiple%20loopholes%20and%20ambiguities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20sugarcane%20prices%20are%20determined%20through%20two%20different%20systems%20in%20India.%20While%20farmers%20of%20sugarcane-growing%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Karnataka%20are%20paid%20through%20what%20is%20called%20a%20State-Advised%20Price%20(SAP)%2C%20the%20FRP%20comes%20into%20work%20in%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Generally%2C%20the%20SAP%20is%20fixed%20without%20any%20big%20variable%20component%20like%20sugar%20recovery%20rates%2C%20and%20has%20historically%20been%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20FRP.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20SAP%20for%20Punjab%20is%20already%20at%20Rs%20391%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20state%20governments%2C%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20have%20increased%20SAP%20for%20political%20gains%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20or%20have%20announced%20bonuses%20on%20top%20of%20the%20SAP.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20using%20the%20FRP%20to%20secure%20an%20electoral%20advantage%20over%20the%20opposition%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20but%20the%20hike%20in%20FRP%20will%20anyway%20not%20matter%20to%20farmers%20of%20SAP-driven%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20353px)%2085vw%2C%20353px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23084149%2Fashwini-chaudhary-monty-mh73Y9oKelk-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sugarcane%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23084149%2Fashwini-chaudhary-monty-mh73Y9oKelk-unsplash.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23084149%2Fashwini-chaudhary-monty-mh73Y9oKelk-unsplash-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23084149%2Fashwini-chaudhary-monty-mh73Y9oKelk-unsplash-683x1024.jpg%20683w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698431%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Ashwini%20Chaudhary(Monty)%2FUnsplash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eeven%20the%20minor%20increase%20in%20FRP%20is%20contingent%20upon%20a%20stricter-than-before%20recovery%20rate.%20While%20the%20new%20FRP%20of%20Rs%20340%20per%20quintal%20of%20sugarcane%20will%20be%20calculated%20at%20Rs%2010.25%25%20recovery%20of%20sugar%2C%20the%20current%20price%20of%20Rs%20315%20is%20being%20calculated%20at%20the%20rate%20of%209.5%25%20recovery.%20Resultantly%2C%20the%20hike%20will%20essentially%20be%20ineffective%20for%20many%20farmers%20whose%20crop%20may%20not%20produce%20the%20increased%20recovery%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ashok%20Chaudhary%2C%20former%20chairman%20of%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Thana%20Bhawan%20Sugar%20Mill%20Society%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrecisely%20for%20such%20variables%2C%20the%20farmers%20of%20western%20UP%20struggled%20to%20get%20the%20SAP%20introduced%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20our%20area%2C%20the%20private%20sugar%20mills%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20recovery%20rates%2C%20and%20sometimes%20actually%20falsified%20them%20to%20deny%20the%20farmers%20their%20actual%20price.%20Now%2C%20UP%E2%80%99s%20SAP%20is%20already%20at%20Rs%20370%20per%20quintal%2C%20much%20better%20than%20the%20new%20FRP%2C%20but%20still%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20any%20profit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SAP%20does%20not%20properly%20factor%20in%20input%20costs%20based%20on%20steep%20inflationary%20pressures%20on%20the%20farmer%2C%20but%20the%20FRP%20which%20is%20calculated%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20minimum%20input%20costs%20is%20even%20worse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20every%20sugarcane%20grower%20should%20get%20at%20least%20Rs%20440%20per%20quintal%20to%20recover%20costs%20and%20make%20a%20marginal%20profit%2C%20forget%20%E2%80%9Cdoubling%20his%20income%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erising%20input%20costs%20every%20year%20have%20worsened%20the%20already%20hard-hitting%20agrarian%20distress%20in%20the%20countryside.%20Neither%20the%20SAP%20nor%20the%20FRP%20factor%20in%20inflationary%20pressures%20properly%2C%20and%20have%20stuck%20to%20old%20formulas%20of%20calculating%20the%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20claims%20that%20an%20average%20farmer%20in%20western%20UP%20holds%20around%200.8%20hectare%20of%20farmland%2C%20which%20produces%20anywhere%20between%20500-550%20quintals%20of%20sugarcane%2C%20if%20other%20variable%20factors%20like%20weather%20conditions%2C%20availability%20of%20water%20and%20electricity%2C%20pest%20attacks%20and%20labour%20charges%20are%20within%20control.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20a%20moment%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20assume%20that%20a%20rare%20situation%20where%20all%20conditions%20of%20the%20government%20like%20recovery%20rate%2C%20quality%20of%20the%20crop%20and%20other%20things%20are%20met%20by%20the%20farmer%2C%20500%20quintals%20of%20sugarcane%20should%20fetch%20him%20Rs%201%2C70%2C000%20according%20to%20the%20new%20FRP.%20Ask%20any%20farmer%2C%20you%20will%20find%20everyone%20must%20have%20spent%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%202-2.5%20lakh%20in%20the%2018-24%20months%20the%20crop%20takes%20to%20mature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20has%20been%20the%20%3Cem%3Emehengai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(price%20rise)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20have%20mostly%20relied%20on%20other%20occupations%20in%20recent%20years%20for%20their%20livelihood%2C%20as%20depending%20on%20farming%20alone%20has%20only%20brought%20them%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimanshu-karan-thapar-msp-ashok-gulati-farmers%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20'MSP%20Subsidy%20for%20Consumers%20Not%20Farmers%2C%20They%20Will%20Diversify%20Crops%20If%20Govt%20Amps%20Up%20Support'%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98MSP%20Subsidy%20for%20Consumers%20Not%20Farmers%2C%20They%20Will%20Diversify%20Crops%20If%20Govt%20Amps%20Up%20Support%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFour%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emost%20sugarcane%20farmers%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20although%20the%20predetermined%20prices%2C%20be%20it%20through%20the%20SAP%20or%20FRP%2C%20are%20cripplingly%20inadequate%2C%20their%20suffering%20is%20compounded%20by%20a%20delay%20in%20payments.%20Most%20sugar%20mills%20in%20UP%20have%20crores%20to%20pay%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20who%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20sell%20their%20crop%20to%20the%20nearest%20sugar%20mills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Union%20and%20many%20state%20governments%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20have%20taken%20various%20measures%20to%20clear%20dues%20to%20the%20farmers%20by%20bailing%20out%20loss-making%20sugar%20mills%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20far%20from%20over.%20The%20payments%20by%20sugar%20mills%20are%20delayed%20by%20years%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20farmers%20are%20perpetually%20caught%20in%20a%20vicious%20circle%20of%20debts%20and%20loans%20against%20mortgages.%20The%20lack%20of%20adequate%20institutional%20loans%20in%20India%20has%20only%20exacerbated%20their%20misery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Planning%20Commission%20member%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Sudhir%20Panwar%2C%20who%20is%20now%20also%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20member%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20always%20had%20a%20step-motherly%20attitude%20towards%20sugarcane%20farmers.%20During%20the%20tenures%20of%20both%20the%20Modi%20and%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20in%20UP%2C%20sugarcane%20prices%20have%20seen%20the%20least%20number%20of%20hikes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20has%20helped%20increase%20the%20prices%20of%20sugar%2C%20(sugarcane%20byproducts)%20ethanol%20and%20molasses%20substantively%20but%20haven%E2%80%99t%20bothered%20to%20match%20the%20inflationary%20rate%20for%20sugarcane%20growers.%20During%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20sugarcane%20prices%20have%20increased%20only%20by%205.7%25%2C%20while%20the%20Centre%20has%20increased%20dearness%20allowance%20for%20government%20employees%20by%2019%25%20and%20has%20also%20offered%20sugarcane%20industry%20multiple%20doles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20UP%20government%20had%20increased%20sugarcane%20prices%20by%20around%2026%25%20in%20its%20tenure%20from%202012%20to%202017%2C%20while%20it%20has%20been%2017.46%25%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20years%20during%20the%20Adityanath-led%20state%20government%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20sugar%20mills%20have%20received%20much%20relief%20in%20the%20correspondent%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20claims%20that%20the%20latest%20hike%20of%20Rs%2025%20per%20quintal%20is%20a%20108%25%20hike%20in%20sugarcane%20prices%20since%202014.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20as%20the%20threshold%20to%20calculate%20the%20price%20has%20always%20been%20abysmally%20low.%20The%20FRP%2C%20if%20I%20am%20right%2C%20is%20calculated%20at%20an%20unreal%20input%20cost%20per%20quintal%20of%20around%20Rs%20110.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20any%20farmer%20who%20can%20even%20start%20sowing%20at%20this%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Panwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20political%20move%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20hike%20at%20a%20time%20when%20farmers%20have%20begun%20yet%20another%20round%20of%20protest%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20political%20move%20by%20the%20Centre.%20The%20hike%20is%20meant%20to%20send%20a%20friendly%20signal%20to%20sugarcane%20farmers%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20two%20biggest%20states%20in%20terms%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20decision%20may%20be%20timely%20for%20the%20Jayant%20Chaudhary-led%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20to%20prevent%20its%20complete%20fall%20from%20grace%2C%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20dangle%20a%20carrot%20in%20front%20of%20his%20traditional%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLD%E2%80%99s%20influence%20is%20restricted%20to%20western%20UP%2C%20a%20sugarcane-growing%20belt.%20Chaudhary%20had%20been%20a%20prominent%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20until%20he%20switched%20camp%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20recently.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20convince%20party%20supporters%2C%20primarily%20comprising%20a%20big%20section%20of%20Jat%20peasantry%20of%20western%20districts%20of%20UP%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20groomed%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20to%20oppose%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20alleged%20anti-farmer%20policies.%20His%20party%20also%20supported%20the%202020-21%20year-long%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20up%20the%20sugarcane%20price%20is%20also%20a%20move%20to%20prevent%20the%20Jat%20farmers%20of%20western%20UP%20to%20join%20ranks%20with%20their%20Sikh%20counterparts%20in%20the%20ongoing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20in%20the%20future.%20Rakesh%20Tikait%2C%20the%20prominent%20western%20UP%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20had%20expressed%20his%20support%20to%20the%20Sikh%20farmers%E2%80%99%20call%20of%20%E2%80%9CDelhi%20Chalo%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20Centre%20should%20immediately%20implement%20the%20MSP%20law%20that%20was%20promised%20to%20them%20in%202021.%20One%20may%20recall%20how%20Tikait%E2%80%99s%20emotional%20outburst%20following%20police%20action%20on%20his%20demonstration%20at%20a%20Delhi%20border%20had%20given%20a%20fresh%20lease%20of%20life%20to%20the%202020-21%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20agitations.%20The%20Centre%20may%20not%20want%20to%20repeat%20the%20same%20mistake%20of%20letting%20the%20two%20most%20prominent%20peasant%20communities%20unite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20move%20may%20also%20placate%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20in%20Maharashtra%20who%20believe%20that%20he%20has%20been%20wronged%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Pawar%20recently%20lost%20his%20party%20symbol%20and%20name%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20to%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20who%20had%20defected%20to%20the%20NDA%20along%20with%20a%20majority%20of%20party%20legislators.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20now%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20exercises%20tremendous%20support%20among%20the%20Marathas%2C%20and%20especially%20the%20sugarcane%20farmers%20in%20the%20community.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20rose%20to%20fame%20and%20stature%20in%20the%201980s%20because%20of%20his%20leadership%20in%20the%20farmers%20movement%20to%20put%20in%20place%20a%20system%20of%20farmer-driven%20cooperative%20sugar%20industry%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%20recently%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20introduce%20a%2010%25%20quota%20for%20Marathas%2C%20in%20yet%20another%20attempt%20to%20placate%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20considerations%20are%20writ%20large%20upon%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20latest%20decision%20to%20hike%20sugarcane%20prices%2C%20even%20if%20it%20may%20matter%20little%20to%20the%20cultivators.%20Yet%2C%20the%20optics-obsessed%20BJP%20succeeds%20in%20its%20intention%2C%20which%20is%20positive%20signaling%20to%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708658017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23084027%2Fashwini-chaudhary-monty-egeN7GYoONs-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsugarcane-price-hike-frp-modi-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20hike%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20multiple%20loopholes%20and%20ambiguities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsugarcane-price-hike-frp-modi-govt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20is%20flexing%20his%20power%20with%20the%20deaths%20of%20his%20opponents%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20may%20also%20be%20highlighting%20the%20weakness%20of%20his%20regime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Putin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7f47390413ab8e1d6453a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20during%20his%20interview%20with%20Tucker%20Carlson%3Cp%3EGAVRIIL%20GRIGOROV%20vias%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVladimir%20Putin%20is%20racking%20up%20a%20string%20of%20strongman%20wins%2C%20including%20the%20death%20of%20opposition%20leader%20Alexey%20Navalny.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Putin's%20brazen%20displays%20of%20power%20highlight%20the%20weakness%20of%20his%20regime%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoing%20after%20his%20opponents%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course%20for%20Putin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20two-year%20anniversary%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-just-had-one-of-his-best-ever-weeks-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVladimir%20Putin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20likely%20behind%20a%20series%20of%20exorbitant%20displays%20of%20his%20authoritarian%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3