9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recent%20deaths%20due%20to%20wild%20animal%20attacks%20have%20sparked%20massive%20protests%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68366869%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68366869.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68366869.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Russia-linked%20smear%20campaign%20against%20Hunter%20Biden%20began%20earlier%20than%20previously%20thought%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hunter%20Biden%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649322241465b60019987d4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20April%2018%2C%202022%3A%20Hunter%20Biden%20during%20the%20White%20House%20Easter%20Egg%20Roll%20on%20the%20South%20Lawn%20on%20April%2018%2C%202022..%3Cp%3EDemetrius%20Freeman%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20KGB%20agent%20handed%20a%20thumb%20drive%20with%20Hunter%20Biden%20disinformation%20to%20an%20aide%20for%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20at%20a%20gala%20event%20in%20May%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20former%20KGB%20agent%20also%20presented%20the%20same%20disinformation%20to%20Justice%20Department%20officials%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20presentation%20marks%20the%20earliest%20known%20instance%20of%20a%20Russia-linked%20source%20pushing%20allegations%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20thumb%20drive%20handed%20by%20a%20foreign%20national%20to%20an%20aide%20traveling%20with%20then-Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20in%202019%20suggests%20that%20efforts%20by%20Russia-linked%20actors%20to%20influence%20the%202020%20US%20presidential%20election%20with%20Hunter%20Biden%20disinformation%20began%20earlier%20and%20were%20broader%20in%20scope%20than%20has%20previously%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20two%20sources%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20thumb%20drive%20containing%20poorly%20sourced%20allegations%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20his%20work%20for%20Burisma%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20energy%20company%2C%20was%20thrust%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20of%20Pompeo's%20aides%20at%20the%20conservative%20Claremont%20Institute's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.claremont.org%2Fevents%2F40-annual-gala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40th%20anniversary%20gala%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Beverly%20Hills%20on%20May%2011%2C%202019.%20The%20man%20pushing%20the%20thumb%20drive%20was%20a%20citizen%20of%20an%20Eastern%20European%20country%20and%20a%20guest%20of%20Claremont.%20He%20was%20also%2C%20for%20a%20time%2C%20an%20FBI%20confidential%20informant%2C%20with%20the%20code%20name%20%26quot%3BRollie.%26quot%3B%20His%20true%20name%20is%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20is%20only%20identifying%20him%20as%20Rollie%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20sources%20who%20provided%20information%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERollie%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20seemed%20unconcerned%20about%20potential%20exposure.%20At%20first%2C%20he%20denied%20knowing%20anything%20about%20Pompeo%20when%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20when%20BI%20sent%20him%20a%20photo%20of%20him%20at%20the%20gala%20with%20Pompeo%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20he%20had%20been%20there.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20publish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20advertising%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22759%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20with%20%26quot%3BRollie%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7e32f6080194819f998af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20with%20%26quot%3BRollie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20KGB%20agent%2C%20at%20a%20Claremont%20Institute%20gala%20on%20May%2011%2C%202019.%20That%20evening%2C%20Rollie%20passed%20a%20thumb%20drive%20containing%20disinformation%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma%20to%20a%20Pompeo%20aide.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20obtained%20by%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERollie%20told%20associates%20and%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20had%20once%20served%20in%20the%20KGB%2C%20the%20Soviet%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20before%20swearing%20loyalty%20to%20the%20country%20where%20he%20now%20resides.%20The%20thumb%20drive%20that%20Rollie%20gave%20Pompeo's%20aide%20contained%20some%20of%20the%20same%20material%20that%20Rollie%20had%20presented%20weeks%20earlier%2C%20in%20January%202019%2C%20in%20a%20briefing%20to%20Justice%20Department%20officials%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20interested%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Rollie%20said%20when%20asked%20over%20WhatsApp%20about%20the%20briefing.%20He%20denied%20that%20he%20gave%20anyone%20a%20thumb%20drive%20at%20the%20Claremont%20Institute%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20obtained%20a%20copy%20of%20slides%20that%20accompanied%20Rollie's%20January%202019%20presentation.%20They%20accuse%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20his%20business%20associates%20of%20engaging%20in%20money%20laundering%2C%20tax%20evasion%2C%20and%20fraud.%20Rollie's%20slides%20offer%20a%20labyrinthine%20wire%20chart%2C%20clippings%20from%20old%20news%20articles%2C%20and%20a%20potpourri%20of%20links%20including%20various%20Ukrainian%20and%20Russian%20websites.%20President%20Biden's%20first%20name%20is%20repeatedly%20misspelled%20as%20%26quot%3BJosef.%26quot%3B%20They%20contain%20no%20evidence%20of%20criminal%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20according%20to%20a%20disclosure%20prepared%20by%20FBI%20whistleblower%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20Rollie's%20handler%2C%20the%20material%20was%20taken%20seriously%20enough%20to%20be%20passed%20on%20to%20FBI%20agents%20in%20Delaware%20who%20were%20investigating%20Hunter%20Biden.%20Also%20included%20were%20some%20Ukrainian-language%20backup%20materials%20which%20Business%20Insider%20has%20not%20reviewed.%20Rollie%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20had%20prior%20contact%20with%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rollie%20presentation%20sheds%20new%20light%20on%20the%20timeline%20of%20efforts%20by%20Russia%20and%20by%20operatives%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20seed%20allegations%20about%20Joe%20Biden's%20relationship%20to%20Burisma%20with%20the%20media%20and%20government%20authorities.%20While%20questions%20about%20the%20propriety%20of%20Hunter's%20lucrative%20Burisma%20work%20in%20Ukraine%20were%20raised%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2015%2F12%2F09%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fcorruption-ukraine-joe-biden-son-hunter-biden-ties.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20early%20as%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20explored%20in%20a%202018%20book%20by%20conservative%20author%20Peter%20Schweizer%2C%20they%20didn't%20explode%20into%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20political%20conversation%20until%20March%202019.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20month%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-impeachment-inquiry%2Fgiuliani-says-state-dept-vowed-investigate-after-he-gave-ukraine-n1061931%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERudy%20Giuliani%20gave%20Pompeo%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20folder%20of%20Hunter%20Biden%20material%20that%20he%20obtained%20from%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20right-wing%20investigative%20reporter%20John%20Solomon%20began%20publishing%20a%20series%20of%20columns%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fnews%2F483600-the-hills-review-of-john-solomons-columns-on-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hill%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20month%20later%2C%20in%20April%202019%2C%20Hunter%20abandoned%20his%20laptop%20at%20a%20Delaware%20repair%20shop%2C%20eventually%20leading%20to%20a%20wave%20of%20revelations%20in%20October%202020%20that%20included%20information%20about%20his%20business%20dealings%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hunter-Burisma%20material%20that%20was%20presented%20in%20January%202019%2C%20and%20again%20on%20the%20thumb%20drive%20given%20to%20Pompeo's%20aide%20in%20May%202019%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20earliest%20known%20case%20of%20Burisma-related%20disinformation%20of%20foreign%20origin%20being%20ingested%20and%20apparently%20taken%20seriously%20by%20members%20of%20the%20US%20intelligence%20community.%20It%20also%20suggests%20a%20third%20channel%20of%202020%20disinformation%20moving%20from%20East%20to%20West%2C%20one%20that%20is%20separate%20from%20the%20previously%20known%20efforts%20that%20went%20through%20Giuliani%20and%20Alexander%20Smirnov%2C%20another%20FBI%20informant%20with%20ties%20to%20Russia%20and%20Eastern%20Europe.%20Smirnov%20was%20indicted%20last%20week%20for%20lying%20to%20the%20FBI%20about%20Hunter%20Biden.%20Prosecutors%20have%20claimed%20in%20court%20filings%20that%20Smirnov%20has%20extensive%20ties%20to%20Russian%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20Hunter%20Biden's%20critics%20have%20focused%20on%20Burisma.%20The%20energy%20company%20paid%20Biden%20around%20%24600%2C000%20a%20year%20during%20a%20period%20that%20overlapped%20with%20his%20father's%20vice%20presidency.%20It's%20unclear%20what%20the%20company%20got%20for%20their%20money%20beyond%20the%20ability%20to%20brag%20about%20an%20indirect%20line%20into%20the%20White%20House.%20But%20almost%20five%20years%20after%20his%20departure%20from%20the%20board%2C%20Hunter%20Biden%20was%20never%20charged%20with%20any%20wrongdoing%20for%20his%20Burisma%20service.%20Instead%2C%20Special%20Counsel%20David%20Weiss%20has%20indicted%20Hunter%20for%20tax%20evasion%20and%20lying%20on%20a%20form%20to%20purchase%20a%20firearm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20about%20Rollie's%20thumb%20drive%20comes%20shortly%20after%20the%20indictment%20of%20Smirnov%2C%20for%20allegedly%20making%20false%20statements%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20in%20June%202020.%20Like%20Smirnov%2C%20Rollie's%20materials%20accuse%20Hunter%20Biden%20of%20involving%20his%20father%20in%20Burisma's%20business%20and%20committing%20a%20vast%20off-the-books%20fraud.%20Smirnov's%20alleged%20lies%20included%20the%20allegation%20that%20Burisma%20officials%20paid%20a%20%245%20million%20bribe%20to%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20were%20memorialized%20in%20an%20FBI%20form%201023%2C%20which%20records%20raw%20reporting%20from%20confidential%20sources%2C%20that%20was%20circulated%20by%20GOP%20Sen.%20Charles%20Grassley.%20The%20thumb%20drive%20incident%20raises%20further%20questions%20about%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20foreign%20actors%20can%20obtain%20access%20to%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20the%20US%20government%20and%20then%20pass%20off%20rubbish%20as%20legitimate%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Pompeo%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20repeated%20requests%20for%20comment.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20Pompeo%20or%20his%20aide%20did%20anything%20with%20the%20material%20on%20the%20thumb%20drive%20after%20receiving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20State%20Department%20official%20who%20served%20under%20Pompeo%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20was%20not%20unusual%20for%20officials%20to%20receive%20random%20material%20from%20people%20they%20meet%20at%20social%20events%2C%20and%20that%20there%20was%20a%20process%20in%20place%20for%20handing%20such%20materials%20off%20to%20in-house%20experts%20for%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Claremont%20Institute%2C%20which%20was%20responsible%20for%20vetting%20the%20gala%20guest%20list%2C%20on%20Thursday%20and%20did%20not%20immediately%20receive%20a%20reply.%20After%202016%2C%20the%20Claremont%20Institute%20drifted%20from%20traditional%20conservative%20politics%20into%20more%20extreme%20territory.%20It%20granted%20a%20fellowship%20to%20MAGA%20troublemaker%20Jack%20Posobiec%2C%20who%20has%20used%20his%20online%20platform%20to%20spread%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20and%20served%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2024%2F01%2F20%2Fus%2Fdei-woke-claremont-institute.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20organizing%20hub%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20backlash%20to%20DEI%20initiatives%20in%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20FBI%20declined%20to%20comment.%20The%20Justice%20Department%20and%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20Buma%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20after%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20reporting%20by%20Anastasiia%20Carrier.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-russia-linked-campaign-to-spread-dirt-about-hunter-biden-and-burisma-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708649878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657273fd7a3c8094d5dadf1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-russia-linked-campaign-to-spread-dirt-about-hunter-biden-and-burisma-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20KGB%20agent%20handed%20off%20a%20thumb%20drive%20with%20disinfo%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20to%20a%20Trump%20official%20at%20a%20Claremont%20Institute%20gala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mschwartz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mattathias%20Schwartz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A111%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-russia-linked-campaign-to-spread-dirt-about-hunter-biden-and-burisma-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2