nly%20nation%20to%20have%20tried%20and%20failed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20previous%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20only%20found%20success%20several%20years%20after%20crashing%20during%20its%20first%20attempt.%20Russia's%20lunar%20lander%20was%20destroyed%20in%20a%20crash%20in%20August%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-moon-probe-landed-upside-down-still-works-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan's%20landed%20upside%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IM-1%20mission%20spacecraft%20floating%20in%20space%20with%20Earth%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d65e9ea3bd891424f90c71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIntuitive%20Machines%20captured%20this%20image%20of%20the%20Odysseus%20moon%20lander%20as%20it%20flew%20away%20from%20Earth.%3Cp%3EIntuitive%20Machines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpaceflight%20is%20hard.%20A%20million%20things%20have%20to%20go%20right%2C%20and%20if%20one%20thing%20goes%20wrong%2C%20you%20can%20still%20have%20a%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vice%20President%20of%20Intuitive%20Machines's%20space%20systems%2C%20Trent%20Martin%2C%20during%20a%20NASA%20press%20briefing%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20only%20about%2050%25%20of%20lunar%20landing%20missions%20succeed.%20While%20technology%20has%20advanced%20a%20lot%20since%20Apollo%2C%20the%20moon's%20treacherous%20terrain%20and%20distance%20from%20Earth%20make%20failure%20pretty%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESpace%20exploration%20goes%20commercial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IM-1%20mission%20is%20part%20of%20NASA's%20new%20deep-space%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20Commercial%20Lunar%20Payload%20Services%20(CLPS)%20program%2C%20the%20government%20space%20agency%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-helping-private-companies-build-business-moon-make-lunar-billions-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutsource%20spacecraft%20design%20to%20private%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20Intuitive%20Machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20that%20companies%20build%20the%20hardware%20and%20NASA%20hitches%20a%20ride%2C%20saving%20taxpayer%20money%20and%20giving%20the%20agency%20more%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIM-1%20wasn't%20the%20first%20time%20NASA%20has%20done%20this.%20For%20its%20last%20lunar%20landing%20attempt%20in%20January%2C%20NASA%20partnered%20with%20the%20Pittsburgh-based%20company%20Astrobotic%20Technology%20to%20send%20its%20Peregrine%20spacecraft%20to%20the%20moon.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-moon-lander-peregrine-burn-up-earth-atmosphere-satellite-astrobotic-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20mission%20did%20not%20succeed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Earth%20photographed%20by%20the%20Intuitive%20Machines'%20Odysseus%20moon%20lander.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d65f89f533b039a885c9a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIntuitive%20Machines'%20Odysseus%20moon%20lander%20beamed%20back%20its%20first%20images%20from%20space%20earlier%20this%20month.%3Cp%3EIntuitive%20Machines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENASA%20has%20several%20CLPS%20missions%20scheduled%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20including%20two%20more%20with%20Intuitive%20Machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Intuitive%20Machines'%20next%20mission%2C%20its%20spacecraft%20is%20scheduled%20to%20launch%20toward%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20again%20in%202024%2C%20this%20time%20to%20deliver%20a%20drill%20designed%20to%20dig%20down%20into%20a%20ridge%20near%20the%20Shackleton%20crater%20to%20look%20for%20ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20later%20this%20year%2C%20a%20different%20Intuitive%20M