ound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20of%20farmer%20unions%20across%20the%20country%20that%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20compelling%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20repeal%20three%20farm%20laws%20during%20their%20year-long%20protest%20in%202020%2C%20decided%20not%20to%20join%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20barriers%20during%20their%20general%20body%20meeting%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20February%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20it%20announced%20its%20own%20parallel%20programmes%2C%20from%20holding%20a%20day-long%20%E2%80%98kisan%20mahapanchayat%E2%80%99%20in%20Delhi%20next%20month%20on%20March%2014%20to%20organising%20a%20tractor%20march%20on%20highways%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20%E2%80%9CDelhi%20Chalo%E2%80%9D%20programme%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20SKM%20splinter%20group%2C%20SKM%20(non-political)%2C%20under%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangarsh%20Committee%20under%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20why%20the%20SKM%20decided%20not%20to%20join%20the%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20told%20the%20media%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20these%20groups%20decided%20to%20march%20for%20Delhi%20without%20consulting%20the%20SKM.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20join%20them%20now%2C%20it%20would%20give%20the%20impression%20that%20we%20are%20going%20there%20to%20disturb%20their%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20SKM%20was%20not%20showing%20unity%2C%20Rajewal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20media%20should%20not%20put%20their%20words%20on%20our%20mouth.%20Our%20focus%20is%20on%20unity%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20all%20farmers.%20Despite%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20Dallewal%20and%20Pandher%20groups%20from%20the%20SKM%2C%20we%20have%20still%20formed%20a%20six-member%20committee%20to%20establish%20coordination%20with%20them%20and%20advance%20our%20common%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajewal%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20whether%20protesting%20farmers%20should%20march%20ahead%20or%20call%20off%20their%20protest%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20strong%20police%20action%20is%20for%20them%20to%20make%2C%20as%20they%20are%20managing%20the%20entire%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20a%20day%20after%20Dallewal%20invited%20all%20farm%20unions%20to%20bolster%20their%20protest%20at%20the%20borders%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20farmer%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20calm%20at%20the%20borders%20since%20their%20Delhi%20march%20remains%20suspended%20till%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20told%20the%20media%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%20that%20they%20would%20announce%20their%20next%20course%20of%20action%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%20announces%20nationwide%20protest%20in%20response%20to%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20death%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20death%20of%2022-year-old%20farmer%20Shubkaran%20Singh%20at%20the%20Khanouri%20border%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20announced%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20scheduled%20for%20February%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20protest%2C%20SKM%20urged%20farmers%20to%20burn%20effigies%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20and%20Haryana%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoginder%20Singh%20Ughrahan%2C%20president%20of%20BKU%20(Ughrahan)%20and%20member%20of%20SKM%2C%20declared%20February%2023%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20day%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20by%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20into%20the%20%E2%80%98murder%E2%80%99%2C%20along%20with%20Rs%201%20crore%20compensation%20for%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20further%20programmes%2C%20another%20SKM%20member%20Avik%20Saha%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2026%2C%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20there%20will%20be%20%E2%80%98tractor%20%3Cem%3Epradarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(demonstration)%20where%20we%20will%20ask%20the%20government%20to%20quit%20WTO.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2014%2C%20an%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Mahapanchayat%20will%20be%20organised%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20in%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20expect%20more%20than%20a%20lakh%20people%20to%20join%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20on%20Thursday%20expressed%20its%20condolences%20for%20the%20passing%20of%20Singh%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20life%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresenting%20the%20House%E2%80%99s%20condolence%20message%2C%20Speaker%20Ram%20Niwas%20Goel%20described%20Wednesday%E2%80%99s%20incident%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20painful.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20the%20allegations%20and%20criticism%20against%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Union%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20said%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20continuously%20working%20and%20dedicated%20towards%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20farmers.%20Just%20yesterday%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20farmers%2C%20the%20fair%20and%20remunerative%20price%20of%20sugarcane%20was%20fixed%20at%20Rs%20340%20per%20quintal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98The%20price%20of%20protest%20must%20not%20be%20death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20death%20of%20Singh%20during%20the%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20march%2C%20Aakar%20Patel%2C%20chair%20of%20board%20at%20Amnesty%20International%20India%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20of%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20occurred%20amid%20a%20ruthless%20crackdown%20by%20the%20state%20authorities%20on%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20in%20India.%20Authorities%20must%20carry%20out%20a%20prompt%2C%20effective%2C%20thorough%2C%20independent%20and%20impartial%20investigation%20into%20the%20cause%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the%20death%20of%20the%20protester%2C%20and%20ensure%20the%20suspected%20perpetrators%20are%20brought%20to%20justice%20through%20fair%20trials%20without%20recourse%20to%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20more%20protests%20planned%20for%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20authorities%20must%20do%20all%20in%20their%20power%20to%20ensure%20that%20people%20can%20peacefully%20voice%20their%20concerns%2C%20without%20fear%20of%20injury%20or%20death.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%20must%20respect%2C%20protect%20and%20facilitate%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20peaceful%20assembly%20in%20line%20with%20its%20international%20human%20rights%20obligations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20price%20of%20protest%20must%20not%20be%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708623177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fa-day-after-farmers-death-skm-announces-wider-programmes-nationwide-protest-set-for-friday%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SKM's%20decision%20came%20a%20day%20after%20all%20farm%20unions%20were%20invited%20to%20bolster%20their%20protest%20at%20the%20borders%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20farmer%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fa-day-after-farmers-death-skm-announces-wider-programmes-nationwide-protest-set-for-friday%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20killed%20after%20barge%20crashes%20into%20bridge%2C%20as%20vehicles%20plunge%20into%20water%