ut-mourners-13078434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alexei%20Navalny's%20mother%20has%20said%20she%20has%20seen%20the%20body%20of%20her%20son%20-%20and%20that%20officials%20are%20trying%20to%20force%20her%20to%20hold%20a%20private%20burial%20ceremony%20without%20mourners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A180%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress-SP%20Alliance%20Seals%20Seat-Sharing%20Deal%20in%20UP%20and%20MP%2C%20but%20Some%20Major%20Challenges%20Remain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22213242%2Fimage-1860.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20have%20finally%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20the%20key%20states%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sealing%20of%20the%20deal%20%E2%80%93%20after%20a%20period%20of%20hectic%20negotiations%2C%20mixed%20signals%20and%20public%20display%20of%20disagreement%20%E2%80%93%20and%20coming%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Frld-ditches-india-for-nda-what-this-means-9157927%2F%5C%22%3E%20exit%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20big%20step%20for%20the%20Opposition%20as%20it%20prepares%20to%20take%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20populous%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20only%20the%20first%20step%20in%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20hectic%20two%20months%20for%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20as%20it%20challenges%20a%20dominant%20BJP%20across%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20candidate%20selection%20to%20building%20a%20common%20narrative%20against%20the%20powerful%20NDA%20alliance%20of%20five%20parties%20in%20the%20state%20and%20coordinating%20strategies%20for%20shared%20public%20meetings%20and%20transfer%20of%20votes%2C%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20%E2%80%93%20a%20leaner%20version%20of%20the%20original%20INDIA%20bloc%20%E2%80%93%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20achieve%20before%20voting%20day%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20compromise%20reached%20by%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20contest%2017%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%2063%20are%20in%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20bank.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20SP%20would%20accommodate%20its%20sole%20remaining%20ally%2C%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kameravadi)%20of%20Pallavi%20Patel%2C%20within%20that%20figure.%20There%20is%20no%20confirmation%20yet%20if%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20has%20finalised%20a%20seat%20for%20the%20Dalit%20leader%20from%20west%20UP%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20(Kanshi%20Ram).%20However%2C%20leaders%20of%20both%20parties%20have%20shown%20openness%20to%20the%20idea%2C%20given%20that%20the%20bloc%20lacks%20a%20Dalit%20face%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20Mayawati-led%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20adamant%20on%20going%20solo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20MP%2C%20where%20the%20SP%20is%20a%20minor%20power%2C%20the%20party%20will%20contest%20only%20one%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20Khajuraho%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20remaining%2028%20seats%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20deal%20came%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2021)%2C%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20uncertainty%20with%20the%20SP%20toying%20with%20its%20ally%20by%20unilaterally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Flok-sabha-polls-sp-announces-11-faces-after-akhilesh-yadav-india-seat-talks-update-101708338835764.html%5C%22%3Ereleasing%20names%20of%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20on%20seats%20claimed%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20SP%20leader%20Rajendra%20Chaudhary%2C%20state%20president%20Naresh%20Uttam%20Patel%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Avinash%20Pande%20and%20state%20president%20Ajay%20Rai%20addressed%20the%20media%20as%20they%20announced%20the%20deal%20in%20Lucknow.%20The%20venue%20was%20a%20hotel%20situated%20near%20the%20offices%20of%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20both%20sides%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20threats%20to%20democracy%2C%20the%20constitution%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech%20in%20the%20country%20under%20the%20Modi%20regime.%20They%20vowed%20to%20fight%20collectively%20and%20campaign%20for%20each%20other%20to%20protect%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20future%2C%20its%20democracy%20and%20constitution%20and%20strengthen%20communal%20harmony%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20issues%20are%20of%20deep%20concern%20to%20the%20health%20of%20the%20democratic%20status%20of%20India%2C%20the%20alliance%20would%20need%20to%20go%20beyond%20rhetoric%20and%20communicate%20to%20the%20electorate%20an%20alternative%20model%20of%20life%20and%20livelihood%20that%20ensures%20their%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20welfare%2C%20if%20they%20aspire%20to%20wean%20away%20support%20from%20the%20BJP%20in%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20complex%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20only%20one%20MP%20and%20two%20MLAs%20in%20a%20state%20where%20it%20once%20ruled%20the%20roost%2C%20should%20be%20content%20with%20the%20seats%20allotted%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20provides%20a%20national%20lens%20to%20the%20contest%20in%20UP%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20social%20calculus%2C%20adds%20little%20to%20the%20arithmetic%2C%20as%20it%20does%20not%20enjoy%20the%20loyalty%20of%20any%20particular%20caste%20group%20or%20region.%20Its%20only%20card%20has%20been%20the%20implicit%20threat%20it%20carries%20of%20dividing%20Opposition%20votes%20if%20it%20contests%20alone%2C%20like%20in%202019.%20However%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%20and%20Gomti%20since%20then%20and%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20was%20inevitable%20for%20any%20serious%20contest%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20the%2017%20seats%20allotted%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20shows%20that%20it%20has%20got%20a%20mixed%20bag%20%E2%80%93%20some%20relatively%20easy%20seats%20and%20some%20extremely%20difficult%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20seats%20allotted%20to%20the%20Congress%20are%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%20the%20pocket%20borough%20of%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%20in%20central%20UP.%20There%20is%20no%20clarity%20yet%20if%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20%E2%80%93%20Rahul%20and%20Priyanka%20%E2%80%93%20will%20contest%20from%20these%20seats%20now%20that%20sitting%20Rae%20Bareli%20MP%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20has%20decided%20to%20get%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20been%20allotted%20the%20Varanasi%20seat%2C%20although%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020)%2C%20SP%2C%20in%20a%20big%20public%20snub%2C%20declared%20a%20candidate%2C%20former%20MLA%20Surendra%20Singh%20Patel%2C%20as%20its%20candidate%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20talks%20had%20failed.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20the%20MP%20from%20Varanasi%20and%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most-watched%20constituencies%20in%20the%20country.%20When%20Rajendra%20Chaudhary%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20SP%20would%20not%20return%20the%20seat%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20follow%20with%20full%20honesty%20the%20understanding%20we%20have%20reached.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20had%20initially%20been%20adamant%20about%20picking%20seats%20based%20on%20the%202009%20formula%2C%20a%20year%20when%20it%20performed%20remarkably%20well%20and%20won%2021%20out%20of%2080%20seats%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20final%20list%20of%20constituencies%20appears%20more%20random.%20The%20Congress%20got%20favourable%20seats%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Saharanpur%20and%20Amroha%2C%20both%20with%20sizeable%20Muslim%20voters%2C%20in%20west%20UP.%20Imran%20Masood%20and%20Kunwar%20Danish%20Ali%20are%20the%20likely%20candidates%20from%20these%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20last%20time%20the%20Congress%20won%20Saharanpur%2C%20Amroha%2C%20Deoria%2C%20Sitapur%2C%20Bulandshahr%20and%20Allahabad%20was%20in%201984%20following%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination.%20These%20were%20included%20in%20the%2017%20seats%20for%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmitabh%20Bachchan%20was%20the%20last%20Congress%20candidate%20to%20win%20in%20Allahabad%2C%20four%20decades%20ago.%20The%20Congress%20will%20also%20contest%20in%20Barabanki%2C%20which%20abuts%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20major%20urban%20centres%20Kanpur%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Jhansi%20and%20Mathura.%20The%20BJP%20won%20Ghaziabad%20by%20more%20than%20five%20lakh%20votes%20in%202019.%20The%20Congress%20candidate%20got%20less%20than%2030%2C000%20votes%20in%20Bulandshahr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20is%20a%20leaner%20version%20of%20the%20formidable%20SP-BSP-RLD%20alliance%20that%20took%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20Even%20without%20the%20BSP%2C%20which%20has%20lost%20its%20way%2C%20the%20SP-RLD-Congress%20combine%20looked%20decent%20and%20balanced%20across%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20exit%20of%20the%20RLD%2C%20the%20entire%20burden%20of%20preventing%20the%20BJP%20from%20winning%20maximum%20seats%20in%20UP%20rests%20on%20the%20SP%20and%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20a%20disastrous%20partnership%20in%202017%20during%20the%20state%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20faces%20many%20challenges.%20First%2C%20arithmetic.%20The%20BJP%20won%20over%2050%25%20votes%20in%20UP%20in%202019.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20added%20two%20more%20allies%20and%20now%20has%20four%20regional%2C%20caste-based%20allies%20with%20command%20over%20votes%20of%20the%20OBC%20Nishads%2C%20Jats%2C%20Kurmis%20and%20Rajbhars.%20This%20provides%20the%20BJP%20a%20solid%20cushion%20to%20offset%20losses%20due%20to%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20when%20the%20SP-RLD-BSP%20fought%20together%2C%20their%20combined%20vote%20share%20could%20not%20cross%2040%25%2C%20though%20in%202014%2C%20when%20they%20fought%20separately%2C%20their%20collective%20vote%20share%20of%2042.9%25%20almost%20matched%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%2043.6%25%20vote%20share.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ally%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneylal)%20won%2073%20of%2080%20seats.%20In%202019%2C%20despite%20a%20combined%20Opposition%2C%20the%20BJP-plus%20won%2064%20of%20these%20seats%20and%20the%20NDA%20vote%20share%20hit%20an%20unsurmountable%20mark%20of%20more%20than%2051%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20demonstrates%20that%20simple%20arithmetic%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20coalitions%20as%20transfer%20of%20vote%20banks%20must%20be%20compatible%20and%20harmonious.%C2%A0%20The%20SP%20has%20lost%20two%20of%20its%20main%20allies%20since%20its%20decent%20performance%20in%202022%2C%20when%20it%20climbed%20from%2047%20to%20over%20110%20assembly%20seats.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20manage%20only%20one%20seat%2C%20Rae%20Bareli.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20lost%20Amethi%20despite%20getting%20support%20from%20the%20SP%20and%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20as%20already%20hinted%20above%2C%20beyond%20arithmetic%2C%20the%20alliance%20needs%20chemistry%2C%20to%20not%20only%20ensure%20transfer%20of%20votes%20but%20also%20to%20attract%20new%20voters.%20This%20means%20their%20top%20leadership%20as%20well%20as%20state%20units%20need%20to%20be%20in%20sync%20on%20issues%20and%20campaign%20strategy.%20Any%20differences%20of%20opinion%20will%20be%20promptly%20exploited%20by%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20time%20running%20out%2C%20how%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20which%20compete%20with%20each%20other%20for%20the%20same%20votes%2C%20will%20drum%20up%20a%20collective%20strategy%20across%20the%20state%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20initially%20agreed%20to%20attend%20the%20Congress%20Nyay%20Yatra%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20but%20on%20February%2019%2C%20he%20took%20a%20step%20back%20and%20said%20he%20would%20join%20it%20once%20seat-sharing%20was%20done.%20Now%20that%20the%20seat-sharing%20is%20complete%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20Yadav%20will%20join%20the%20Congress%20Yatra%20in%20west%20UP%2C%20probably%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20no%20doubt%20the%20alliance%20was%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20What%20has%20been%20achieved%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20bare%20minimum.%20The%20lean%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20must%20understand%20that%20it%20is%20a%20limited%20alliance.%20It%20must%20set%20realistic%20goals%20as%20it%20faces%20a%20BJP%20that%20is%20ruthless%20and%20superior%20in%20resources%2C%20organisation%2C%20media%20control%20and%20has%20a%20rallying%20face%20under%20Modi.%20Social%20arithmetic%20also%20dictates%20that%20the%20SP-Congress%20set%20specific%20goals%20and%20a%20focused%20strategy%20on%20winnable%20seats%20rather%20than%20stretching%20itself%20thin%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20appear%20flamboyant.%20Their%20task%20should%20be%20to%20reduce%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20seat%20share%20rather%20than%20go%20overboard%20with%20campaigning%20on%20seats%20that%20are%20difficult%20to%20win.%20There%20is%20plenty%20the%20two%20parties%20can%20learn%20from%20their%202017%20alliance%2C%20when%20they%20spent%20too%20much%20time%20showcasing%20the%20personal%20harmony%20between%20their%20leaders%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93UP%20%3Cem%3Eke%20ladke%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20should%20instead%20focus%20on%20forcefully%20communicating%20to%20the%20voters%20why%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20change%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20both%20the%20parties%20must%20lead%20from%20the%20front.%20The%20SP%20has%20fielded%20members%20of%20its%20ruling%20family%20on%20traditional%20seats%2C%20with%20Akhilesh%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20Shivpal%20set%20to%20debut%20in%20Budaun%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20had%20initially%20been%20allotted%20to%20his%20nephew%20and%20former%20MP%20Dharmendra%20Yadav%2C%20who%20could%20contest%20from%20Azamgarh%20or%20Kannauj.%20The%20SP%20has%20already%20declared%2031%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20lagging%20in%20this%20regard.%20If%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20don%E2%80%99t%20contest%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%20it%20will%20amount%20to%20a%20massive%20moral%20defeat%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20would%20concede%20its%20strongest%20political%20forts%20in%20the%20country%20without%20a%20fight.%20A%20non-Gandhi%20candidate%2C%20whether%20they%20win%20or%20lose%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20much%20of%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20larger%20narrative.%20The%20two%20seats%20are%20not%20ordinary%20constituencies%20but%20loaded%20with%20history%20and%20legacy%20of%20what%20the%20Congress%20stands%20for.%20To%20send%20a%20message%20of%20confidence%20to%20their%20cadre%20and%20voters%20and%20to%20galvanise%20their%20support%20base%2C%20the%20siblings%20must%20take%20the%20plunge%2C%20put%20themselves%20on%20the%20line%20and%20contest%20from%20these%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20the%20alliance%20must%20set%20the%20agenda%20and%20push%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20answer%20difficult%20questions%20on%20unemployment%2C%20jobs%2C%20farmers%20income%2C%20recruitment%20exams%2C%20dilution%20of%20reservation%2C%20which%20are%20all%20burning%20issues%20currently%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%20of%20the%20police%20constable%20exam%20and%20an%20ongoing%20600-day%20plus%20dharna%20by%20job%20seekers%20from%20OBC%20castes.%C2%A0%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20issues%20that%20the%20Opposition%20can%20tap%20into%20to%20bust%20the%20myths%20of%20a%20prosperous%20UP%20under%20the%20double-engine%20of%20the%20BJP.%20The%20aspirational%20youth%20and%20the%20unhappy%20farmer%20can%20be%20the%20fulcrum%20of%20that%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixth%2C%20another%20challenge%20facing%20the%20alliance%20is%20the%20prospect%20of%20communal%20polarisation.%20Whenever%20two%20Opposition%20parties%20get%20together%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20able%20to%20project%20it%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20mainstream%20media%2C%20that%20they%20are%20uniting%20just%20to%20consolidate%20the%20Muslim%20votes.%20The%20alliance%20must%20intercept%20this%20and%20overload%20the%20narrative%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20uniting%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits.%20That%20is%20their%20best%20armour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20coming%20together%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20already%20cemented%20the%2020%25%20Muslim%20vote%20which%20is%20decisive%20on%20a%20number%20of%20seats.%20Now%2C%20they%20need%20to%20dent%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20backward%20caste%20and%20Dalit%20vote.%20To%20do%20that%2C%20the%20parties%20must%20communicate%20to%20the%20voters%20why%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20necessary%20for%20them%20and%20what%20is%20the%20material%20gain%20they%20get%20out%20of%20it.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20trishul%20of%20Ram%20(Hindutva)%2C%20Ration%20(welfare%20schemes)%20and%20Representation%20(more%20space%20for%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20in%20power)%20is%20a%20potent%20formula%2C%20and%20to%20counter%20that%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20Congress%20would%20need%20to%20take%20it%20head%20on%20through%20%3Cem%3Ejati%2C%20jobs%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejunta%20ke%20sawaal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20side-stepping%20the%20trap%20of%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20of%20PDA%20%5B%3Cem%3EPicchde%3C%2Fem%3E%20(backward%20classes%20or%20OBCs)%2C%20Dalits%20and%20%3Cem%3EAlpsankhyak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(minorities)%5D%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20vocal%20stand%20on%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20issues%20must%20align%20into%20a%20consolidated%20narrative.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20SP%20must%20speak%20the%20same%20language.%C2%A0%20During%20his%20ongoing%20yatra%20in%20UP%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20raised%20the%20issues%20of%20unemployment%20among%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20and%20their%20lack%20of%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mayawati%20has%20remained%20adamant%20and%20decided%20to%20go%20alone%2C%20how%20her%20voters%20behave%20will%20be%20of%20interest%20to%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20SP-Congress%20combine.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20big%20surprise%20if%20she%20fields%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Muslims%20to%20play%20up%20a%20narrative%20that%20SP%20is%20not%20honest%20towards%20their%20interests.%20Note%20that%20the%20party%20recently%20drew%20flak%20from%20two%20OBC%20leaders%2C%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Pallavi%20Patel%2C%20and%20a%20former%20MP%20Saleem%20Shervani%20for%20fielding%20two%20non-political%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20candidates%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20while%20ignoring%20Dalits%2C%20OBCs%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20major%20challenge%20for%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20as%20a%20three-way%20contest%20favours%20the%20ruling%20party%20as%20the%20two%20Opposition%20blocs%20would%20be%20competing%20for%20the%20same%20votes.%20Maurya%20and%20Shervani%20have%20quit%20SP%2C%20while%20Patel%20rebelled%20by%20joining%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20when%20there%20was%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20speculations%20that%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%20wants%20to%20join%20the%20alliance.%20How%20the%20SP%20fights%20for%20the%20sizable%20Dalit%20votes%2C%20especially%20in%20west%20UP%2C%20would%20be%20seen.%20But%20there%20are%20signs%20that%20the%20party%20is%20willing%20to%20experiment%20boldly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20has%20recently%20opened%20to%20the%20public%2C%20and%20for%20a%20general%20seat%2C%20the%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Ffor-its-dalit-outreach-sp-puts-forward-ayodhya-leader-with-long-party-electoral-record-8535208%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20nominated%3C%2Fa%3E%20veteran%20MLA%20and%20Dalit%20leader%20Awadesh%20Prasad.%20It%20is%20uncommon%20for%20a%20Dalit%20to%20contest%20unreserved%20seats.%20In%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20where%20the%20SP%20won%20all%20five%20seats%20in%202022%2C%20the%20party%20has%20nominated%20senior%20OBC%20leader%20Lalji%20Verma%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20sitting%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20out%20of%20the%2064%20seats%20the%20BJP%20and%20Apna%20Dal%20held%2C%20they%20won%2025%20by%20over%20two%20lakh%20votes%2C%20and%2021%20by%20over%20one%20lakh%20to%20two%20lakh%20votes.%20This%20makes%20these%2045-odd%20seats%20potentially%20difficult%20to%20overturn.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Opposition%20must%20invest%20more%20in%20winnable%20seats%20and%20retain%20their%20old%20strongholds.%20In%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20Opposition%2C%20though%20losing%20in%20the%20overall%20race%2C%20performed%20well%20in%20certain%20regions.%20They%20won%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Ghazipur%2C%20five%20out%20of%20nine%20in%20Jaunpur%2C%20five%20out%20of%20seven%20in%20Ballia%2C%20three%20out%20of%20four%20in%20Mau%2C%20all%2010%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20four%20out%20of%20five%20in%20Basti%2C%20all%20five%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20two%20out%20of%20five%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20three%20out%20of%20six%20in%20Barabanki%2C%20all%20three%20in%20Kaushambi%2C%20four%20out%20of%20eight%20in%20Bijnor%2C%20seven%20out%20of%20nine%20in%20Shamli%20and%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20five%20out%20of%20six%20in%20Moradabad%2C%20three%20out%20of%20four%20in%20Sambhal%20and%20three%20out%20of%20six%20in%20Budaun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20seat-sharing%20was%20finalised%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20the%20alliance%20was%20to%20save%20the%20constitution%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20to%20provide%20the%20%E2%80%9C90%25%20PDA%E2%80%9D%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708618069000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22213242%2Fimage-1860.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-sp-alliance-seals-seat-sharing-deal-in-up-and-mp-but-some-major-challenges-remain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sealing%20of%20the%20deal%20is%20only%20the%20first%20step%20in%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20hectic%20two%20months%20for%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20as%20it%20challenges%20a%20dominant%20BJP%20across%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20UP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-sp-alliance-seals-seat-sharing-deal-in-up-and-mp-but-some-major-challenges-remain%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pale%2C%20drawn%20and%20behind%20bars%2C%20what%20remains%20of%20Russian%20opposition's%20attempts%20to%20rally%20supporters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708615440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-vladimir-kara-murza_6465382.jpg%3F20240222153950%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpale-drawn-and-in-a-siberian-prison-what-remains-of-russias-opposition-attempts-to-rally-supporters-13078390%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20remains%20of%20Russia's%20opposition%20through%20the%20stuffy%2C%20bureaucratic%20prism%20of%20a%20Moscow%20courtroom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpale-drawn-and-in-a-siberian-prison-what-remains-of-russias-opposition-attempts-to-rally-supporters-13078390%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20Skier%20Killed%2C%20Six%20Others%20Rescued%20After%20Avalanche%20in%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Gulmarg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17121316%2Fimad-clicks-Dg6tMlfSOQ4-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Russian%20skier%20was%20killed%20while%20six%20others%20were%20rescued%20on%20Thursday%20(February%2022)%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20Mt%20Afarwat%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Gulmarg%20ski%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20seven%20skiers%20from%20Russia%20had%20planned%20a%20routine%20adventure%20run%20in%20Khilanmarg%20area%20of%20Gulmarg%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20the%20area%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%2C%20burying%20all%20of%20them%20along%20with%20a%20local%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20is%20prone%20to%20avalanches%2C%20and%20skiers%20go%20there%20on%20their%20own%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20news%20of%20the%20tragedy%20reached%20the%20Gulmarg%20Ski%20Patrol%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20managing%20sports%20activities%20on%20the%20slopes%20of%20the%20north%20Kashmir%20ski%20resort%2C%20a%20rescue%20team%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20area%20and%20helicopters%20were%20also%20deployed%20to%20help%20in%20the%20search%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20collaborative%20effort%20between%20the%20Gulmarg%20Ski%20Patrol%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20other%20state%20agencies%20resulted%20in%20the%20successful%20rescue%20of%20the%20group%20as%20well%20as%20one%20local%20guide%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slain%20skier%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Hanten%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Moscow.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20body%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20Tangmarg%20sub-district%20hospital%20for%20post-mortem%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20a%20local%20police%20officer%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Embassy%20of%20Russia%20in%20India%20maintains%20constant%20contact%20with%20the%20local%20authorities.%20The%20avalanche%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20observed%20in%20the%20region%20since%20February%2017.%20On%20February%2021%2C%20a%20medium%20danger%20level%20avalanche%20warning%20was%20issued%20for%20Baramulla%20district%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20Russian%20embassy%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20a%20slope%20on%20Mt%20Afarwat%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20avalanche%2C%20showed%20a%20private%20chopper%20landing%20near%20tall%20mounds%20of%20snow.%20The%20local%20guide%20remained%20missing%20for%20some%20time%20but%20he%20was%20rescued%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20edition%20of%20Khelo%20India%20Games%20or%20National%20Winter%20Games%2C%20which%20were%20inaugurated%C2%A0%20in%20Gulmarg%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20were%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20avalanche%2C%20officials%20said.%20The%20games%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20till%20February%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20was%20also%20in%20Gulmarg%20when%20the%20tragedy%20happened%20and%20he%20posted%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20the%20skiers%20were%20skiing%20off%20the%20piste%20or%20groomed%20slopes%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98back%20country%E2%80%99.%20Days%20like%20today%20remind%20us%20that%20while%20the%20skiing%20is%20fun%2C%20the%20fresh%20powder%20exhilarating%20%26amp%3B%20the%20visuals%20spectacular%2C%20skiing%20is%20not%20without%20its%20dangers%20%26amp%3B%20risk%20to%20lives.%20Praying%20that%20all%20the%20missing%20skiers%20are%20found%20alive%20%26amp%3B%20the%20reports%20of%20a%20casualty%20end%20up%20being%20unfounded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricketing%20legend%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20also%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Gulmarg%20which%20has%20recorded%20a%20bumper%20snowfall%20this%20week%20after%20a%20prolonged%20spell%20of%20dry%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20has%20brought%20cheer%20for%20the%20hotel%20industry%20and%20other%20local%20stakeholders.%20After%20the%20bumper%20snowfall%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20there%20have%20been%20frequent%20traffic%20jams%20on%20Gulmarg-Tangmarg%20road%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20influx%20of%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNearly%20all%20the%20hotels%20in%20Gulmarg%20are%20full%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20the%20trend%20to%20continue%20for%20another%20two-three%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20tourism%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Kashmir%20this%20week%2C%20officials%20have%20been%20issuing%20avalanche%20warnings%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20A%20massive%20avalanche%20struck%20Sonamarg%20health%20resort%20in%20central%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20month%20but%20there%20were%20no%20fatalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20skiers%20have%20faced%20the%20wrath%20of%20deadly%20avalanches%20in%20Gulmarg.%20In%20February%20last%20year%2C%20two%20Polish%20skiers%20were%20killed%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20were%20rescued%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20the%20%E2%80%98backco