2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99re%20propelling%20ourselves%20into%20an%20unknown%20climate%20future.%20Evolved%20to%20thrive%20in%20an%20ice%20age%2C%20our%20bodies%20aren%E2%80%99t%20built%20for%20a%20very%20hot%20world.%20The%20heat%20threshold%20for%20human%20health%20and%20safety%20is%20measured%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fscience%2F2022%2Fjul%2F31%2Fwhy-you-need-to-worry-about-the-wet-bulb-temperature%5C%22%3Ewet-bulb%20temperature%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94a%20measurement%20that%20combines%20heat%20and%20humidity%E2%80%94%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psu.edu%2Fnews%2Fresearch%2Fstory%2Fhumans-cant-endure-temperatures-and-humidities-high-previously-thought%2F%5C%22%3Eabove%2031%C2%BAC%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20100%25%20humidity.%20Above%20these%20thresholds%2C%20the%20human%20body%20simply%20cannot%20cool%20itself%20fast%20enough.%20Prolonged%20physical%20exertion%20in%20such%20extreme%20heat%20can%20lead%20to%20coma%20or%20death.%20Repeatedly%20labouring%20under%20these%20conditions%20even%20for%20shorter%20spells%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F06%2F18%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Findia-heat-death.html%5C%22%3Edetrimental%20to%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkarger.com%2Fanm%2Farticle%2F74%2FSuppl.%2525203%2F38%2F42811%2FClimate-Change-and-the-Kidney%5C%22%3Elinked%20to%20kidney%3C%2Fa%3E%20disease.%20And%20new%20studies%20suggest%20heat-related%20mortality%20may%20be%20even%20more%20closely%20linked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2073-4433%2F14%2F12%2F1710%5C%22%3Enights%20that%20remain%20very%20warm%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs43247-023-00897-0%5C%22%3Esimply%20daytime%20temperature%3C%2Fa%3E%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstances%20of%20such%20high%20temperatures%20had%20been%20vanishingly%20rare%20in%20the%20human%20past.%20But%20they%E2%80%99re%20becoming%20more%20common%20as%20we%20heat%20the%20planet%20and%20melt%20its%20ancient%20reservoirs%20of%20ice.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20cool%20but%20humid%20monsoon%20weather%20that%20once%20provided%20relief%20from%20summer%E2%80%99s%20heat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cseindia.org%2Frising-heat-stress-in-india-are-we-prepared--11329%5C%22%3Eisn%E2%80%99t%20cooling%20down%20as%20much%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20used%20to%2C%20instead%20presenting%20higher%20wet-bulb%20conditions%20and%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8589686%2F%5C%22%3Enotably%20affecting%3C%2Fa%3E%20health%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0160412024000473%5C%22%3Emortality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20will%20happen%20in%20a%20world%20even%20hotter%20by%20one%20or%20two%20degrees%3F%20Humans%20have%20never%20lived%20in%20such%20a%20hot%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ll%20do%20well%20to%20remember%20that%20we%20are%20the%20children%20of%20the%20Pleistocene%2C%20forged%20by%20the%20power%20of%20fire%2C%20molded%20by%20a%20world%20of%20ice.%20We%20remain%20existentially%20dependent%20upon%20some%20balance%20of%20both.%20But%20those%20of%20us%20acculturated%20to%20industrial%20civilisation%20have%20lost%20all%20awareness%20of%20this.%20In%20our%20insatiable%20and%20reckless%20pursuit%20of%20fire%E2%80%94to%20power%20steam%20engines%2C%20internal%20combustion%20engines%2C%20rockets%2C%20and%20almost%20everything%20else%20we%20use%20to%20build%20out%20the%20human%20world%E2%80%94we%E2%80%99re%20blithely%20sacrificing%20our%20world%20of%20ice.%20Combusting%20mountainous%20quantities%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20far%20beyond%20just%20cooking%20our%20food%2C%20is%20now%20consuming%20the%20planet%20itself%2C%20reshaping%20its%20climate%20and%20ecosystems%20in%20ways%20that%20increasingly%20threaten%20human%20and%20other%20life.%20Having%20forgotten%20our%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbecoming-human-forged-by-fire%5C%22%3Ecomplex%20relationship%20to%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20seem%20now%20to%20have%20taken%20on%20a%20new%20and%20blinding%20obsession%20with%20ourselves%E2%80%94a%20dangerous%20hubris%20that%20pervades%20industrial%20age%20cultures%2C%20entailing%20gigantic%20costs%20that%20become%20more%20apparent%20everyday.%20We%20have%20forgotten%20that%20we%20remain%20subject%20to%20the%20same%20laws%20and%20limits%20that%20govern%20all%20living%20systems%20on%20Earth.%20What%20this%20means%20for%20us%20and%20our%20planet%20will%20be%20the%20subject%20of%20next%20week%E2%80%99s%20essay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUsha%20Alexander%20trained%20in%20science%20and%20anthropology.%20After%20working%20for%20years%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20now%20lives%20in%20Gurugram.%20She%E2%80%99s%20written%20two%20novels%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Legend%20of%20Virinara%3Cem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EOnly%20the%20Eyes%20Are%20Mine%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708611091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22192550%2FMorteratsch_glacier_1-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbecoming-human-shaped-by-ice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ice%20age%20shaped%20what%20we%20are.%20And%20in%20it%20we%20thrived.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbecoming-human-shaped-by-ice%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%E2%80%99s%20Biofertiliser%20Helps%20Farmers%20Cut%20Costs%20by%2050%25%2C%20Earns%20Him%20Over%20Rs%201%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETejraj%20Sahu%2C%20a%20farmer%20hailing%20from%20the%20Bargarh%20district%20of%20Odisha%2C%20recalls%20his%20best%20day%20ever%20to%20be%20in%20March%202023.%20It%20was%20the%20day%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342788%2Fyellow-dates-farming-in-india-engineer-quits-job-to-become-an-agripreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20farmer%3C%2Fa%3E%20trusted%20his%20paddy%20field%20with%20a%20new%20fertiliser.%20The%20harsh%20scorching%20sun%20coupled%20with%20unseasonal%20rains%20and%20reduced%20water%20holding%20capacity%20of%20the%20field%20had%20spelt%20trouble%20for%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20crops%20for%20some%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20when%20things%20were%20looking%20bleak%2C%20he%20got%20to%20know%20about%20a%20new%20fertiliser%20%E2%80%98Navyakosh%E2%80%99%20that%20was%20making%20waves%20in%20the%20farming%20community%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahu%20immediately%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20its%20creator%20Akshay%20Shrivastav%20from%20Kushinagar.%20He%20wanted%20to%20understand%20if%20the%20fertiliser%20lived%20up%20to%20what%20it%20promised%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342247%2Fmangaluru-man-quits-corporate-career-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20yield%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2020%20percent%20while%20cutting%20the%20cost%20by%2050%20percent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20assured%20him%20it%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20trust%2C%20Akshay%20told%20him%20he%20would%20be%20shipping%20him%20one%20tonne%20of%20the%20product%20(20%20bags%20of%20fertiliser)%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20try%20it%20to%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20Sahu%2C%20who%20was%20thrilled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20that%20followed%2C%20not%20only%20did%20this%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%E2%80%9D%20product%20help%20Sahu%E2%80%99s%20paddy%20field%20tremendously%2C%20but%20it%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342126%2Fhow-to-grow-water-lily-at