20with%20a%20student%20leader%2C%20were%20kidnapped%20at%20gunpoint%20by%20unidentified%20men%20near%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20Manipur%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20organisations%20and%20student%20bodies%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20appealed%20for%20their%20immediate%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20other%20student%20leader%20was%20released%20later%20that%20day%20in%20a%20village%20in%20the%20Imphal%20West%20district%2C%20Haridev%20Sharma%20was%20kept%20in%20custody%20by%20the%20kidnappers%20for%2024%20hours%20before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F2%2F22%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Feb-21-Kongbrailatpam-Haridev-a-student-leader-who-was-abducted-in-front-of.html%23%2Fgoogle_vignette%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20was%20released%20in%20Imphal%20on%20February%2022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20some%20groups%20demanding%20Haridev%E2%80%99s%20release%2C%20the%20abductors%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kh.%20Pambei%20faction%20of%20the%20armed%20group%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF-P)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnenow.in%2Fnorth-east-news%2Famsu-president-kidnapped-at-manipur-university-gate.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethough%20the%20outfit%20has%20not%20claimed%20any%20responsibility%20for%20this%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UNLF-P%20is%20currently%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20kidnapping%20incident%20happened%20when%20both%20student%20leaders%20were%20heading%20home%20after%20attending%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Manipur%20issue%20at%20the%20university%2C%20where%20they%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20student%20community%20was%20being%20affected%20by%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELawyers%20protest%20inside%20court%20complex%20to%20protest%20firing%20of%20tear%20gas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20capital%20city%20witnessed%20state%20police%20and%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20(RAF)%20resorting%20to%20firing%20tear%20gas%20within%20a%20court%20complex%20in%20Imphal%20to%20control%20an%20angry%20protest%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20group%20of%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2021%2C%20the%20police%20had%20brought%20to%20the%20Cheirap%20court%20six%20persons%20accused%20of%20looting%20arms%20recently%20from%20the%20India%20Reserve%20Battalion%20(IRB)%20headquarters%20in%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20men%20belong%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedia%20reports%20from%20Imphal%20said%20a%20scuffle%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20women%20and%20the%20security%20personnel%20after%20the%20lower%20court%20remanded%20all%20the%20accused%20to%2015-day%20judicial%20custody.%20The%20women%20demanded%20their%20immediate%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnable%20to%20control%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20state%20police%20brought%20in%20the%20RAF.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20tear%20gas%20was%20used%20to%20disperse%20the%20crowd%2C%20a%20day%20later%2C%20lawyers%20from%20the%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukhrultimes.com%2Fmanipur-lawyers-stage-sit-in-protest-against-chaos-created-in-court-complex%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheld%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20within%20the%20court%20premises%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20condemn%20the%20police%20action%20on%20the%20women%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20state%20institute%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20into%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%20high%20court%20modifies%20controversial%20March%202023%20order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20on%20February%2021%2C%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fmanipur-high-court-withdrawn-direction-meiteis-inclusion-st-list-250174%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20significant%20development%2C%20modified%20its%202023%20order%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20had%20directed%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20to%20consider%20including%20the%20Meitei%20community%20into%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20triggers%20of%20the%20unrest%20that%20Manipur%20has%20been%20witnessing%20since%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20single-judge%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Golmei%20Gaiphulshillu%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20review%20petition%20on%20the%20earlier%20order%20passed%20by%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20M.V.%20Muralidharan%2C%20withdrew%20the%20order%2C%20highlighting%20the%20point%20that%20a%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20led%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20had%20recently%20taken%20strong%20exception%20to%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Manipur%20high%20court%20heard%20the%20case%20this%20past%20February%2021%20since%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stay%20the%20March%2027%20order%20of%20Justice%20Muralidharan%2C%20as%20an%20appeal%20before%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20had%20already%20been%20filed%20by%20groups%20including%20the%20original%20petitioner%2C%20the%20Meitei%20Tribal%20Union.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisplaced%20persons%20say%20rations%20stopped%3B%20ITLF%20demands%20officials%20leave%20Churachandpur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Kuki-dominated%20Churachandpur%2C%20people%20staying%20in%20the%20115%20relief%20camps%20across%20the%20district%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20have%20begun%20an%20indefinite%20strike%20demanding%20that%20their%20rations%20be%20continued%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20refugees%20have%20told%20local%20media%20that%20their%20weekly%20ration%20supply%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-idps-on-strike-as-food-supply-mysteriously-halts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20stopped%20%E2%80%98without%20any%20reason%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rations%2C%20which%20include%20both%20food%20and%20non-food%20items%2C%20are%20distributed%20to%20relief%20camps%20through%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20every%20Monday%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20past%20Monday%20(February%2019)%2C%20the%20rations%20didn%E2%80%99t%20arrive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20a%20mob%20had%20burnt%20the%20Churachandpur%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC)%E2%80%99s%20office%20and%20residence%2C%20leaving%20the%20town%20in%20complete%20disarray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20violence%20was%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20persons%20during%20another%20mob%20attack%20at%20the%20district%20police%20superintendent%20(SP)%E2%80%99s%20office%20a%20day%20earlier%20(a%20few%20hours%20before%20midnight).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mob%20attack%20at%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20office%20was%20triggered%20by%20a%20suspension%20order%20to%20a%20police%20constable%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20after%20a%20video%20clip%20went%20viral%20allegedly%20showing%20him%20with%20armed%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnagalandpost.com%2Findex.php%2F2024%2F02%2F17%2Fdc-office-torched-in-churachandpur-2-killed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENagaland%20Post%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2