Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChemotherapy%20destroys%20all%20fast-growing%20cells%20like%20cancerous%20tumours.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20it%20also%20destroys%20fast-growing%20hair%20follicles%20as%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20differentiate%20between%20healthy%20and%20cancerous%20cells.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20cap%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fit%20properly%2C%20then%20the%20entire%20scalp%20will%20not%20be%20cooled%2C%20causing%20high%20chances%20of%20hair%20loss%20in%20that%20area.%20This%20destroys%20the%20main%20purpose%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Raghuveer%20decided%20to%20design%20a%20cap%20that%20could%20accommodate%20all%20head%20sizes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20launched%20his%20company%20Stemtech%20Medical%20Devices%20and%20innovated%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20where%20a%20universal%20cap%20was%20designed%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%20from%20chemotherapy%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20his%20innovation%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20is%20installed%20in%2018%20hospitals.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5